Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.72,0:00:50.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,时间轴/后期：包大人

Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.60,0:02:07.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好了, 全队保持在视线内\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Alright team, stay in sight of each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.98,0:02:10.56,Chinese,,0,0,0,,今天要让美航局自豪\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Let's make NASA proud today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.58,0:02:12.08,Chinese,,0,0,0,,那儿什么样, 沃特尼?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}How's it looking over there, Watney?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.12,0:02:14.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,嗯, 你肯定乐意听到\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Well, you'll be happy to hear that in
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.38,0:02:19.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,区块14到28里的颗粒都特别粗糙\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}grid section 14 to 28, the particles were phenomenally coarse,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.43,0:02:22.74,Chinese,,0,0,0,,到了29, 这儿的......这儿的颗粒好一些\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}and on 29, they're.... they're much finer,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.76,0:02:24.97,Chinese,,0,0,0,,应该是理想的化学分析样本\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}which should be ideal for chemical analysis.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.00,0:02:26.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,哦, 哇, 大伙儿听到没有?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Oh, wow. Did everybody hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.53,0:02:29.61,Chinese,,0,0,0,,马克刚发现了灰尘, 我们是不是要通知媒体了?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Mark just discovered dirt. Should we alert the media?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.64,0:02:31.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好了, 你今天做什么了, 马丁内斯?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}It's alright. What're you doing today, Martinez?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.31,0:02:33.41,Chinese,,0,0,0,,一直在确保飞行器立着?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Making sure that the MAV is still upright?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.44,0:02:35.71,Chinese,,0,0,0,,呃, 我想你知道目视检查仪器\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Well, I like you know that visual inspection of the equipment
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.74,0:02:37.49,Chinese,,0,0,0,,对于任务成功可是至关重要\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}is imperative to mission success.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.51,0:02:40.80,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我也要报告飞行器还立着\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I also like to report that the MAV is still upright.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.83,0:02:42.99,Chinese,,0,0,0,,沃特尼, 你的频道一直开着\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Watney, you're keep leaving your channel open,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.02,0:02:45.11,Chinese,,0,0,0,,导致马丁内斯回应\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}which leads to Martinez responding,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.13,0:02:48.22,Chinese,,0,0,0,,导致我们都听见了, 导致本小姐很烦\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}which leads to all our listening, which leads to me being annoyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.25,0:02:51.12,Chinese,,0,0,0,,收到马丁内斯, 队长想请你\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Roger that.   Martinez, the captain would like you to please...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.14,0:02:53.13,Chinese,,0,0,0,,关上你的伶牙俐齿\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}shut your smart mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.41,0:02:56.85,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们喜欢用不一样的词来形容马丁内斯的嘴\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}We prefer to use a different adjective to describe Martinez's mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.87,0:03:00.89,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 哟, 刚才贝克是骂了我嘛? - 叫贝克博士, 是的\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- Oh, did Beck just insult me? - Dr. Beck, and, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.91,0:03:03.41,Chinese,,0,0,0,,只要你一声令下, 指挥官\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I'll be happy to turn the radios off from here, commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.45,0:03:04.85,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我很乐意把它关了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Just say the word.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.87,0:03:07.53,Chinese,,0,0,0,,嘿, 约翰森保持通话是整个......\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Hey, Johanssen. Constant communication is the whole...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.55,0:03:09.27,Chinese,,0,0,0,,让他闭嘴\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Shut him off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.91,0:03:14.39,Chinese,,0,0,0,,替我的老乡抱歉了, 沃格尔\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Apologise for my countrymen, Vogel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.41,0:03:17.83,Chinese,,0,0,0,,接受道歉我们需要多少样本, 指挥官?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Accepted. How many samples do we need, commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.85,0:03:20.89,Chinese,,0,0,0,,7组, 每组一百克\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}7, a hundred grams each.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.44,0:03:28.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们有个任务更新, 风暴预警\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}We have a mission update. Storm warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.93,0:03:31.78,Chinese,,0,0,0,,指挥官, 你得进来, 你肯定想看看这个\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Commander, you should come inside. You're going to want to see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.81,0:03:34.03,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 什么东西? - 风暴预警\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- What is it? - Storm warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.05,0:03:37.83,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我在早上的简报里看到了, 我们会赶在风暴之前回舱\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I saw that in this morning's briefing. We'll be inside before it hits.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.86,0:03:40.60,Chinese,,0,0,0,,没错, 他... 他们更新了估算\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Yeah. They- They upgraded their estimate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.63,0:03:42.98,Chinese,,0,0,0,,风暴要严重得多\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}The storm is going to be a lot worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.75,0:03:51.29,Chinese,,0,0,0,,马丁内斯, 风暴看起来怎么样?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Martinez, how's it look?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.86,0:03:53.54,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不妙\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.03,0:03:58.88,Chinese,,0,0,0,,直径1200千米, 偏角24.41度\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}1200 km in diameter bearing 24.41 degrees
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.90,0:04:00.38,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这是直奔着我们来啊\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}That's trekking right towards us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.40,0:04:05.14,Chinese,,0,0,0,,根据现在的估算, 估计力度为8600牛\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Base on current estimation, estimated force of 8600 Newtons.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.17,0:04:08.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 终止力度呢? - 7500牛\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- What's the abort force. - 7500.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.34,0:04:11.53,Chinese,,0,0,0,,只要超过, 飞行器就会翻\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Anything more than that and the MAV will tip.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.56,0:04:14.80,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 我们撤吗? - 启动终止程序\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- Do we scrub? - Begin abort procedure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.83,0:04:19.14,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们还在估算临界误差是多少......我们能不能等等结果?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}We are estimating where the marginal error would be... could we wait it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.17,0:04:21.12,Chinese,,0,0,0,,等等结果吧\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Let's wait it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.31,0:04:24.14,Chinese,,0,0,0,,等等结果吧\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Let's wait it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.19,0:04:26.91,Chinese,,0,0,0,,指挥官\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.30,0:04:29.15,Chinese,,0,0,0,,准备紧急脱离\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Prep emergency departure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.17,0:04:32.57,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 指挥官 - 我们撤, 这是命令\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- Commander. - We're scrubbed, that's an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.65,0:04:45.12,Chinese,,0,0,0,,马丁内斯, 起飞还需要多长时间?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Martinez, how long before take off?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.14,0:04:46.89,Chinese,,0,0,0,,10分钟\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}10 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.59,0:04:51.38,Chinese,,0,0,0,,能见度几乎为零\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Visibility is almost zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.40,0:04:54.05,Chinese,,0,0,0,,谁走散了, 就追踪我宇航服的信号\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Anyone gets lost, home in on my suit's telemetry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.07,0:04:56.34,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 你准备好了? - 好了!\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- You ready? - Ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.49,0:05:02.22,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 指挥官, 你还好吗? - 我很好\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- Commander, are you okay? - I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.49,0:05:29.19,Chinese,,0,0,0,,指挥官, 现在10度了, 飞行器正在向12.3度倾斜\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Commander, we're at 10 degrees, and the MAV's going to tip at 12.3
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.22,0:05:32.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,嘿!我们也许能让飞行器立住\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Hey! We might be able to keep the MAV from tipping.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.74,0:05:34.01,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们怎么做?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.03,0:05:37.03,Chinese,,0,0,0,,用太阳能电站的电缆作牵引绳!\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Use the cables from the solar farm as guylines!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:39.25,Chinese,,0,0,0,,用火星车当锚!\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Anchor it with a Rover!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.27,0:05:40.68,Chinese,,0,0,0,,小心!\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.55,0:05:43.42,Chinese,,0,0,0,,啊啊啊啊!\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Aahhhhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.45,0:05:45.13,Chinese,,0,0,0,,沃特尼!\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Watney!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.03,0:05:48.64,Chinese,,0,0,0,,警告：检测到宇航服破损\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}WARNING SUIT BREACH DETECTED.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.66,0:05:50.33,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 怎么了? - 他被击中了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- What happened? - He was hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.36,0:05:51.74,Chinese,,0,0,0,,沃特尼, 回话\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Watney, report.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.77,0:05:54.46,Chinese,,0,0,0,,失去信号之前, 他的失压警报响了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Before we lose telemetry, his decompression alarm went off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.48,0:05:56.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 约翰森, 你上次看见他是在哪儿? - 他离线了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- Johanssen, where did you last see him? - He's offline.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.27,0:05:58.51,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 我不... 我不知道他在哪儿 - 他宇航服上的生理指标怎么样?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- I can't, I don't know where he is. - What are the vitals on his suit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:06:00.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 他不在线, 他不在线 - 没用, 我们完全失去了沃特尼的信号\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- He's offline. He's offline. - Negative. Complete lost of signal on Watney.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.86,0:06:01.98,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 米契? - 在\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- Mitch? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.01,0:06:04.42,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他能在失压下挺多久?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}How long can he survive decompression?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.45,0:06:06.11,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不到一分钟\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Less than a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.14,0:06:08.68,Chinese,,0,0,0,,一列纵队, 向西前进\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Line up. Walk west.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.70,0:06:11.49,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他可能倒下了, 我们别踩到他\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}He maybe prone, we don't want to step over him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.52,0:06:18.21,Chinese,,0,0,0,,指挥官, 现在10.5度了, 向11度倾斜\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Commander, we're at 10.5 degrees, tilting to 11.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:19.86,Chinese,,0,0,0,,有一阵强风\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}We got a gust of wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.89,0:06:21.11,Chinese,,0,0,0,,收到\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Copy that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.14,0:06:23.31,Chinese,,0,0,0,,全体都有, 追踪马丁内斯的宇航服\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Everyone, home in on Martinez's suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.34,0:06:26.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你们会回到气密舱, 进去, 准备发射\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}It'll get you to the airlock. Get in, prep for launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.20,0:06:27.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,那你怎么办, 指挥官?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}What about you, commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.55,0:06:29.67,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我要再找一会儿\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I'm going to search a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.69,0:06:32.66,Chinese,,0,0,0,,别呆着了, 走!\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Keep moving. Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.41,0:06:38.79,Chinese,,0,0,0,,沃特尼, 沃特尼, 回话\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Watney. Watney, report.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.81,0:06:42.71,Chinese,,0,0,0,,飞行器11.6度了, 来一阵小阴风我们就翻了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}The MAV is at 11.6 degrees. Once good gust and we're tipping.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.73,0:06:44.52,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如果要翻, 你就发射\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}If it tips, you launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.55,0:06:46.15,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你真以为我会抛下你?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}You really think I'm going to leave you behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.18,0:06:48.43,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这是命令, 马丁内斯\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}That's an order, Martinez.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.45,0:06:49.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,马克!\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.42,0:06:53.67,Chinese,,0,0,0,,马克, 能听到吗?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Mark. Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.86,0:06:57.45,Chinese,,0,0,0,,马丁内斯, 防撞雷达行吗?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Martinez, what about the proximity radar?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.48,0:06:59.48,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它能不能检测到, 沃特尼的宇航服\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Could that detect, Watney's suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:01.31,Chinese,,0,0,0,,呃, 它是用来检测轨道里的赫尔墨斯号的\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Uh. It's made to see the Hermes in orbit,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.33,0:07:03.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而不是一件衣服里的一小片铁\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}not a little piece of metal put in a single suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.43,0:07:04.96,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 试试吧 - 收到\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- Give it a try. - Roger.
