Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.12,0:25:45.58,Chinese,,0,0,0,,显然不包括\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}the notable exception of...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.26,0:25:49.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,马丁内斯的个人物品\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Martinez's personal items.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.18,0:25:51.80,Chinese,,0,0,0,,对不起, 马丁内斯, 如果你不想让我翻你的东西\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I'm sorry, Martinez, if you didn't want me to go through your stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.82,0:25:55.26,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你就不应把我丢在这颗荒星上等死\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}you shouldn't left me for dead on a desolate planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.40,0:25:57.81,Chinese,,0,0,0,,话说, 我估计你也不会在意\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}By the way, I'm figuring you're going to be fine with this,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.83,0:26:00.48,Chinese,,0,0,0,,考虑到我现在的状况\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}given my present situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.65,0:26:03.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,靠你了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.83,0:26:40.48,Chinese,,0,0,0,,那么, 是的, 我炸到自己了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}So, yeah. I blew myself up.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.50,0:26:42.35,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我猜最可能是\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Best guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.92,0:26:45.49,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我忘了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I forgot to...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.51,0:26:48.85,Chinese,,0,0,0,,考虑额外的氧气\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}account for the excess oxygen that...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.22,0:26:53.19,Chinese,,0,0,0,,供我呼吸, 之前在计算的时候\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I've been exhaling when I did my calculations,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.31,0:26:55.54,Chinese,,0,0,0,,因为我蠢\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}because I'm stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.14,0:27:00.35,Chinese,,0,0,0,,是啊, 只要我的耳朵停止耳鸣\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Yeah, I'm going to get back to work here,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.37,0:27:03.48,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我还要回来接着做\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}just as soon as my ear stop ringing.
