Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.16,0:27:14.74,Chinese,,0,0,0,,加州理工的5个人, 试着做\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}5 guys at Caltec, trying to make
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.77,0:27:17.69,Chinese,,0,0,0,,火箭燃料, 几乎烧掉了自己的宿舍\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}rocket fuel and they nearly burned down their dorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.71,0:27:21.69,Chinese,,0,0,0,,学校没有开除他们, 而是把他们赶到附近的农场里\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}And rather than expel them, banished them to a nearby farm
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.72,0:27:23.83,Chinese,,0,0,0,,让他们继续研究\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}tell them to keep working.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.36,0:27:26.77,Chinese,,0,0,0,,于是我们就有了太空计划\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}And then we have a space program.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.52,0:27:31.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,成了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.06,0:28:49.79,Chinese,,0,0,0,,嘿, 你好\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Hey, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.69,0:29:03.42,Chinese,,0,0,0,,上帝垂青美国, 让马克参与我们的太空计划\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}The nation was blessed, to have Mark serving in our space program.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.45,0:29:05.71,Chinese,,0,0,0,,在沉痛悼念他的同时\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}While his lost will be deeply felt,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.73,0:29:08.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,美航局的诸位都将坚持不懈\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}the men and women of NASA will soldier forth,
