Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.47,0:29:20.23,Chinese,,0,0,0,,确保他的牺牲没有白费\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}To ensure his sacrifice will not be in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.15,0:29:39.04,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我觉得你的演讲很不错, 就是顺带一说\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I thought you gave a lovely speech, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.41,0:29:44.79,Chinese,,0,0,0,,﹣我需要你批准调用卫星 - 想都别想\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- I need you to authorize my satellite time. - It's not going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.86,0:29:46.78,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们被资助了5次阿瑞斯任务\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}We're funded for 5 ARES missions.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.81,0:29:49.07,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我认为我能让议会批准第6个\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I think I can get congress to authorize a 6th.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.10,0:29:51.44,Chinese,,0,0,0,,听着, 阿瑞斯3号才18个太阳日就撤了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Look, ARES 3 evac'd after 18 Sols.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.47,0:29:53.69,Chinese,,0,0,0,,那儿, 那儿还搁着一半任务的物资呢\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}There's- There's half a mission worth of supplies up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.71,0:29:56.26,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我只要付出普通任务的一小部分代价就可以卖掉它\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I can sell it at a fraction of the cost of a normal mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.29,0:29:58.59,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我只要知道, 我们的财产还剩下多少\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}And all I have to know is, what's left of our assets.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.61,0:30:00.43,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你不是唯一一个需要调用卫星的人\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}You're not the only one who needs satellite time.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.45,0:30:02.56,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们阿瑞斯4号的供应任务马上就要开始\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}We got the ARES 4 supply missions coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.57,0:30:04.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们应该多关注斯基阿帕雷利陨石坑\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}We should be focusing on the Schiaparelli crater.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.73,0:30:07.27,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好吧, 我们有12颗卫星在上面飞, 肯定能富余出来几小时的\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Okay, we got 12 satellites up there, surely we can spare a few hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.30,0:30:09.25,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不是调用卫星的问题, 文斯\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}It's not about satellite time, Vince.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.27,0:30:11.04,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们是公有领域组织\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}We're a public domain organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.06,0:30:13.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 我们在这件事上要透明 - 好吧\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- We need to be transparent on this. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.12,0:30:14.92,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们把卫星瞄向居住舱那一霎\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}The second we point the satellites to the Hab,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.94,0:30:18.14,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我就已经把马克·沃特尼尸体的照片播放给全世界了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I broadcast pictures of Mark Watney's dead body to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.17,0:30:19.62,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你在担心公关问题?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}You're afraid of a PR problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.65,0:30:22.69,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我当然担心公关问题, 还提什么任务?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Of course I'm afraid of a PR problem. Another mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.72,0:30:25.29,Chinese,,0,0,0,,议会连一个曲别针都不会给我们报销\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Congress won't reimburse us for a paper clip
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.31,0:30:28.53,Chinese,,0,0,0,,只要我们把死掉的宇航员挂在华盛顿邮报的首页上\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}if I put a dead astronaut out on the front page of the Washington Post.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.56,0:30:31.54,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他也不能不翼而飞啊, 泰迪我是说, 他不会......\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}He's not going anywhere, Teddy. I mean, he's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.57,0:30:33.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他不会降解掉的\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}he's not going to decompose.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.30,0:30:35.22,Chinese,,0,0,0,,知道吧, 他会永远在那儿\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}You know, he's going to be up there forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.25,0:30:37.73,Chinese,,0,0,0,,气象学家估计他会被沙子覆盖\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Meteorology estimates that he'll be covered in sand
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.76,0:30:39.86,Chinese,,0,0,0,,在正常的天气活动下只需要一年\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}from normal weather activity within a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.88,0:30:41.77,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们不能等上一年, 我们有活儿要干\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}We can't wait a year, we got work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.79,0:30:45.54,Chinese,,0,0,0,,阿瑞斯5号都不会在5年内发射, 我们时间充裕\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}ARES 5 won't even launch for 5 years, we've plenty of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.56,0:30:47.05,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.74,0:30:49.21,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.84,0:30:52.04,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好吧, 考虑一下\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Okay, consider this.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.74,0:30:54.38,Chinese,,0,0,0,,现在\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.40,0:30:56.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,全世界站在我们这边\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}the world is on our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.18,0:30:58.13,Chinese,,0,0,0,,对沃特尼家人的同情\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Sympathy for the Watney family.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.20,0:31:00.69,Chinese,,0,0,0,,阿瑞斯6号可以让他落叶归根\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}ARES 6 can bring his body home
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.71,0:31:03.52,Chinese,,0,0,0,,现在, 我们不说这就是任务的目的\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Now. We don't say that's the purpose of the mission,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.55,0:31:05.41,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不过要明确这是任务的一部分\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}but we make it clear that would be a part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.44,0:31:07.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如果我们这样描述\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}If we frame it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.19,0:31:11.19,Chinese,,0,0,0,,议会会给予更多支持, 但等上一年可就不会了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}More support from congress, but not if we wait a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.21,0:31:13.93,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们等上一年, 就没人鸟你了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}We wait a year nobody gives a shit.
