Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.53,0:32:15.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,啥?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.56,0:32:31.99,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你好, 保卫处\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Hi, security.
