Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.02,0:32:33.69,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我是卫星通信的明迪·帕克\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}This is Mindy Park in SatCom.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.72,0:32:36.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我要紧急连线文森特·卡普尔\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I need the emergency contact for Vincent Kapoor.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.94,0:32:38.66,Chinese,,0,0,0,,对, 他\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Yes, him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.93,0:32:41.17,Chinese,,0,0,0,,对, 紧急\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Yes, it's an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.83,0:32:49.05,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 有多确定? - 100%\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- How sure? - A 100%
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.07,0:32:51.59,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你扯淡呢吧?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}You got to be shitting me?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.61,0:32:53.45,Chinese,,0,0,0,,证明给我看\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Prove it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.20,0:32:56.71,Chinese,,0,0,0,,首先\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}For a start.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.61,0:32:59.80,Chinese,,0,0,0,,天阳能板被清掉了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Solar panels have been cleaned.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.83,0:33:02.01,Chinese,,0,0,0,,可能是风刮走的\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}They could've been cleaned by wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.03,0:33:03.25,Chinese,,0,0,0,,回放\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Back it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.28,0:33:04.48,Chinese,,0,0,0,,看火星车2号\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Look at Rover 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.50,0:33:07.07,Chinese,,0,0,0,,根据记录, 路易斯指挥官把它开出来, 在第17太阳日\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}According to the logs, Command Lewis took it out, Sol 17,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.10,0:33:09.30,Chinese,,0,0,0,,插在居住舱充电\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}plugged it into the Hab to recharge.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.32,0:33:10.69,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它被挪动了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}It's been moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.72,0:33:12.83,Chinese,,0,0,0,,她可能忘了把挪动记录下来了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}She could have forgotten to log the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.85,0:33:14.12,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不, 不太可能\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}No. Not likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.14,0:33:15.47,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们为什么不直接问路易斯\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Why don't we just ask Lewis.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.49,0:33:17.42,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们直接现在用飞船通讯问她呗\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Let's get on CAPCOM and ask her directly right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.44,0:33:19.47,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不, 不, 如果沃特尼真的活着\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}No, no. If Watney is really alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.50,0:33:21.48,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们不要让阿瑞斯3号成员知道\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}we don't want the ARES 3 crew to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.50,0:33:23.41,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你, 你怎么能不告诉他们?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}How- How can you not tell them?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.44,0:33:25.47,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他们还有10个月的航程回家\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}They have another 10 months on their trip home.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.50,0:33:28.53,Chinese,,0,0,0,,太空旅行很危险, 他们需要警觉且不能分心\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Space travel is dangerous, they need to be alert and undistracted.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.55,0:33:30.03,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是, 他们已经以为他死了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}But, they already think he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.05,0:33:33.10,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他们发现落下一个大活人肯定会不知所措\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}And they'd be devastated to find out they left him there alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.13,0:33:35.49,Chinese,,0,0,0,,抱歉, 不过你没有考虑周全\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I'm sorry but you have not thought this through.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.51,0:33:37.82,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我是说, 我们, 我们要怎么说?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I mean, what- what are we going to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.84,0:33:42.01,Chinese,,0,0,0,,亲爱的美国, 还记得那个被我们弄死的了还办了特别好的葬礼的宇航员吗?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Dear America, remember that astronaut we killed and had a really nice funeral for?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.04,0:33:43.82,Chinese,,0,0,0,,结果是他还活着, 我们把他扔在火星了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Turns out he's alive, and we left him on Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.85,0:33:46.14,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们的锅, 真挚的美航局\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Our bad, sincerely NASA.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.16,0:33:49.22,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我是说, 你意识到山雨欲来了吗?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I mean, do you realise the shit storm that's about to hit us?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.24,0:33:51.49,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们该怎么对付公众\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}How're we going to handle the public.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.79,0:33:54.56,Chinese,,0,0,0,,法律上讲, 我们有24个小时来公布这些照片\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Legally, we have 24 hours to release these pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.58,0:33:55.99,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们发表一份声明\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}We release a statement with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.02,0:33:58.60,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们不希望要让人们自己去琢磨\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}We don't want people working it out on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.63,0:33:59.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好的, 长官\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.74,0:34:02.13,Chinese,,0,0,0,,听着, 如果我没算错, 他会在我们救到他之前\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Look, if my math is right, he's going to starve to death
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.15,0:34:04.42,Chinese,,0,0,0,,就会饿死\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}long before we can help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.46,0:34:09.07,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你无法想象他在那儿都经历着什么\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}You can't imagine what he is going through up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.09,0:34:11.11,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我是说, 他离家5000万英里远\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I mean, he's 50 million miles away from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.13,0:34:14.27,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他以为孑然一身, 他以为我们放弃了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}He thinks he's totally alone. He thinks we gave up on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.65,0:34:17.68,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这会让一个人怎样, 心理学上讲?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}And what does that do to a man, psychologically?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.01,0:34:21.12,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他现在究竟在想什么呢?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}What the hell is he thinking right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.72,0:34:27.75,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我一定会死在这儿\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I'm definitely going to die out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.86,0:34:32.35,Chinese,,0,0,0,,只要我再听一首哥特嘻哈迪斯科\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}If I have to listen to anymore goth hop disco music.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.38,0:34:36.89,Chinese,,0,0,0,,天哪, 路易斯指挥官, 你就不能带一些这个世纪的东西吗?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}My god, Commander Lewis, couldn't you have packed anything from this century?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.76,0:34:40.99,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不, 我不, 我不要再《舞力无限》了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}No, I'm not. I'm not going to turn the beat around.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.01,0:34:43.04,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我拒绝\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I refuse to.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.70,0:34:49.91,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你们已经尝试过用哪些方式和马克·沃特尼联系?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}What attempts have been made to make contact with Mark Watney?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.93,0:34:51.57,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们正在努力\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}We're working on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.59,0:34:53.64,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他有充足的供给来求生吗?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Does he have enough supplies to survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.67,0:34:55.38,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们会调查清楚\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}We'll be looking into that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.41,0:34:58.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这对贵局有什么影响? 您是否准备辞职?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}What does this say about the agency? Are you going to resign?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.43,0:34:59.34,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.37,0:35:00.49,Chinese,,0,0,0,,桑德斯博士......\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Dr. Sanders...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.10,0:35:07.80,Chinese,,0,0,0,,是时候想长远一些了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}It's time to start thinking long term.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.83,0:35:10.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,美航局的下一个任务是阿瑞斯4号\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}The next NASA mission is ARES 4
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.21,0:35:13.19,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它应该在斯基亚帕雷利陨石坑登陆\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}and it's suppose to land at Schiaparelli crater,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.21,0:35:15.66,Chinese,,0,0,0,,3200公里远\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}3200 km away.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.69,0:35:17.25,Chinese,,0,0,0,,三千\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}32
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.85,0:35:19.91,Chinese,,0,0,0,,两百公里\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}hundred kilometers.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.94,0:35:22.92,Chinese,,0,0,0,,4年后, 阿瑞斯小队来的时候\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}In 4 years, when the next ARES crew arrives,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.95,0:35:24.82,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我得在这儿\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I'll have to be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.85,0:35:27.55,Chinese,,0,0,0,,也就是说我得去陨石坑\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Which means I have to get to the crater.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.09,0:35:31.01,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好吧, 那么问题来了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Okay, so here's the rub.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.03,0:35:35.97,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我有1台能用的火星车, 设计最大里程为25公里\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I've got 1 working Rover, designed to go a max distance 35 km.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.00,0:35:39.82,Chinese,,0,0,0,,使用之前电池要在居住舱充电\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Before the battery has to be recharge at the Hab.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.85,0:35:41.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这是问题一\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}That's problem A.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.04,0:35:48.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,问题二, 完整走这一趟要花掉我大约50天\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Problem B, is this journey is going to take me roughly 50 days to complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.74,0:35:51.57,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以, 我得活50天下来\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}So, I got to live for 50 days
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.60,0:35:56.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,火星车里有个微型生命维持装置, 有微型面包车那么大\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}inside a Rover with marginal life support, the size of a small van.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.31,0:35:57.78,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}So.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.81,0:36:01.74,Chinese,,0,0,0,,在这种悲催情况下, 我只剩下一个选择\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}In the face of overwhelming odds, I'm left with only 1 option.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.28,0:36:05.87,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我得搞搞科研把这破事儿解决了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I'm going to have to science the shit out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.16,0:36:35.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好, 所以, 成功了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Okay. So, a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.55,0:36:44.13,Chinese,,0,0,0,,通过搜刮1号车, 我把电量增加了一倍\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I've double battery life, by scavenging Rover 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.84,0:36:48.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是, 如果我使用加热器\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}But, if I use the heater,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.98,0:36:54.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,每天就会耗掉一半的电量\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I will burn through half of my battery every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.07,0:36:59.56,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如果我不用加热器, 我就会......\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}If I do not use my heater, I will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.99,0:37:03.34,Chinese,,0,0,0,,被热力学定律慢慢杀死\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}slowly killed by the laws of Thermodynamics.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.37,0:37:07.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我很想现在就把问题解决了, 不过......\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I would love to solve this problem right now, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.66,0:37:11.42,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不巧, 我的蛋蛋都冻僵了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}unfortunately, my balls are frozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.13,0:37:15.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不行了, 就这样吧, 就这样吧\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I can't. I'm calling it. I'm calling it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.47,0:37:31.21,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好消息是, 我可能有办法解决我的取暖问题了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Good news, I may have a solution to my heating problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.24,0:37:36.29,Chinese,,0,0,0,,坏消息是, 那我就必须把放射性同位素温差发电器挖出来\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Bad news, it involves me digging up the radioisotope thermoelectric generator.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.32,0:37:40.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如果我还记得没错, 训练时其中一课的名字就是\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Now, if I remember my training correctly, One of the lessons was titled:
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.39,0:37:43.61,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不要把那个大钚盒子挖出来, 马克\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Don't dig up the big box of plutonium, Mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.64,0:37:48.05,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我明白, 同位素电池对宇宙飞船来说是好东西, 但如果在人类身边裂了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I get it, RTGs are good for spacecraft, But if they rupture around humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.08,0:37:49.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,那人就死翘翘了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}no more humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.22,0:37:51.59,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这就是为什么我们到这儿就把它埋了起来\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Which is why buried it when we arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.62,0:37:52.97,Chinese,,0,0,0,,还插了个旗子\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}And planted that flag,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.00,0:37:56.81,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这样我们就不会蠢到不小心又和它亲密接触\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}so we can never be stupid enough to accidentally go near it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.83,0:37:59.52,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不过, 只要我不打破它\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}But, as long as I don't break it,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.03,0:38:02.64,Chinese,,0,0,0,,工程后勤部大声说了：“毛事儿都没有”\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Elmo did said 'Everything will be fine.', out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.66,0:38:05.32,Chinese,,0,0,0,,听我说, 关键就是, 我再也不冷了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Look, the point is, I'm not cold anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.35,0:38:08.05,Chinese,,0,0,0,,当然, 我也可以想成, 其实\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}And sure, I could choose to think about the fact that I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.08,0:38:12.68,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我很暖和是因为我身后有跟着一个正在衰变的放射性同位素\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}warm because I have a decaying radioactive isotope riding right behind me,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.70,0:38:15.04,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但现在我手头有更大的问题\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}But right now I got bigger problems on my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.07,0:38:19.75,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我把路易斯指挥官个人硬盘的每一个文件都翻了一遍\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I've showered every single data file on Commander Lewis personal drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.79,0:38:24.79,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这真真儿是她最不迪斯科的歌了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}This is officially the least disco song she owns.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.00,0:39:00.58,Chinese,,0,0,0,,沃特尼要去哪儿?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Where is Watney going?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.61,0:39:03.01,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这个, 我们认为他在准备一个行程\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Well, we think he is preparing for a journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.03,0:39:05.25,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他在进行定量的测试\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}He's been conducting equal amount of test .
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.28,0:39:08.91,Chinese,,0,0,0,,开着2号火星车一次比一次远\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Taking the Rover 2 out for longer and longer trips each time.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.66,0:39:13.52,Chinese,,0,0,0,,去哪儿?为什么他不待在相对安全的居住舱?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}To what end? Why would he leave relative safety of the Hab?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.54,0:39:16.57,Chinese,,0,0,0,,嗯, 我们认为他打算去阿瑞斯4号发射点\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Well, we think he plans to travel to the Ares 4 launch site
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.60,0:39:19.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,从而与我们取得联系, 不过这会很冒险\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}in order to make contact with us, but it would be a dangerous gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.79,0:39:22.61,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但如果我们能和他对话, 我们会告诉他留在原地\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}But, if we could talk to him, we would tell him to stay put
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.64,0:39:27.46,Chinese,,0,0,0,,并相信我们会竭力带他活着回家\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}And to trust that we're doing everything in our power to bring him home alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.49,0:39:29.29,Chinese,,0,0,0,,非常感谢\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.82,0:39:33.92,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不要说“带他活着回家”, 文森特\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Don't say 'Bring him home alive', Vincent.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.95,0:39:36.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你知道吗, 这些采访一点也不轻松\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}You know what, these interviews aren't easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.19,0:39:39.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但愿没有问题, 我都尽可能说得正面积极了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}God forbid, I try to say something proactive and positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.78,0:39:40.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,安妮!安妮!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.73,0:39:43.29,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不再让文森特上电视了, 收到\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}No more Vincent on TV. Copy that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.32,0:39:46.89,Chinese,,0,0,0,,76千米, 我没看错吧?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}76 kilometers. Am I reading that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.91,0:39:48.29,Chinese,,0,0,0,,您在问我吗?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Are you asking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.31,0:39:49.34,Chinese,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.36,0:39:50.67,Chinese,,0,0,0,,是, 长官\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.69,0:39:53.80,Chinese,,0,0,0,,马克从居住舱径直向外开了2个小时车\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Mark drove 2 hours straight away from the Hab,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.83,0:39:55.74,Chinese,,0,0,0,,短暂下车活动, 然后又开了2小时\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Did a short EVA and then drove for another 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.76,0:39:58.68,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们认为下车活动是换电池\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}We think the EVA was to change batteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.71,0:40:01.60,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他没载着充氧器或者再生水装置?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}He didn't load up the oxygenator or the water reclaimer?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.62,0:40:04.03,Chinese,,0,0,0,,每41个小时会有17分钟的间隔\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Every 41 hours, there is a 17 minute gap.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.06,0:40:06.57,Chinese,,0,0,0,,轨道运动就会这样, 所以......\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}It's just the way the orbits works, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.59,0:40:09.39,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们有可能漏掉了什么\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}it's possible that we missed something.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.42,0:40:11.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我要间隔降到4分钟\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I want that gap down to 4 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.42,0:40:15.65,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我会给你全部权限来管理卫星以及调整轨道\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I'm giving you total authority over satellite trajectories and orbital adjustments.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.68,0:40:17.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,实现它\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Make it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.43,0:40:18.74,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.77,0:40:21.03,Chinese,,0,0,0,,咱们假设帕克小姐没有漏掉什么\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Let's assume Ms. Park didn't miss anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.05,0:40:24.59,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以, 马克没有前往阿瑞斯4号, 暂且\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}So, Mark is not going to Ares 4, yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.61,0:40:28.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但他很聪明, 明白了这是他惟一的机会\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}But he's smart enough to figure out that is his only chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.03,0:40:31.06,Chinese,,0,0,0,,布鲁斯, 我们的先行补给最早能什么时候到达?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Bruce, what's the earliest we can get a pre- supply there?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.09,0:40:34.03,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这个嘛, 鉴于地球和火星之间的距离\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Well, with the positions of the Earth and Mars,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.06,0:40:36.34,Chinese,,0,0,0,,要用9个月\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}It'll take 9 months.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.37,0:40:38.77,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而且要先用6个月来建造装置\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}And it'll takes 6 months to build them in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.80,0:40:40.29,Chinese,,0,0,0,,3个月\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}3 months.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.32,0:40:41.34,Chinese,,0,0,0,,3?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}3?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.37,0:40:43.80,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你会说这不可能, 然后我会发表一个讲话\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}You're going to say it's impossible, and then I'm going to make a speech
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.82,0:40:46.59,Chinese,,0,0,0,,讲讲你们实验室成员的杰出能力\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}about the blinding capabilities of the JPL team,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.61,0:40:49.22,Chinese,,0,0,0,,然后你们就会在脑子里算算数, 说一些话\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}And then you're going to do the math in your head, And say something
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.24,0:40:51.19,Chinese,,0,0,0,,比如：“一个人加班会很可怕”\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}like, "The overtime alone would be a nightmare."
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.21,0:40:53.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,一个人加班会很可怕\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}The overtime alone would be a nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.27,0:40:56.37,Chinese,,0,0,0,,开工吧, 我会想办法给你们酬劳的\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Get started. I'll find you the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.39,0:40:58.73,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们得告诉小队\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}We need to tell the crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.76,0:41:01.74,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 米契, 我们讨论过了 - 不, 是你在讨论\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- Mitch, we've discussed this. - No, you discussed this.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.77,0:41:05.25,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我才是决定怎样对小队最好的人\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I'm the one who decides what's best for the crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.40,0:41:08.39,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他们理应知道\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}They deserve to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.15,0:41:11.15,Chinese,,0,0,0,,一旦有实际的救援方案, 我们就告诉他们\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Once there's a real rescue plan, we'll tell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.17,0:41:12.93,Chinese,,0,0,0,,否则, 待议\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Otherwise, it's moot.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.95,0:41:15.21,Chinese,,0,0,0,,布鲁斯有3个月来把装备搞定\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Bruce has 3 months to get the payload done.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.24,0:41:17.53,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这才是现在的重点\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}That's all that matters right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.56,0:41:19.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们会尽力的\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}We will do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.20,0:41:21.67,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你不尽力马克就死了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Mark dies if you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.16,0:41:26.58,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这些土豆我已经种了48太阳日了, 所以......\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}It's been 48 Sols since I planted the potatoes, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.61,0:41:28.96,Chinese,,0,0,0,,现在该收获、种新的了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Now it's time to reap and re- sow.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.98,0:41:31.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它们长得比我想的还好\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}They grew even better than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.39,0:41:34.91,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我现在有400株健康土豆\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I now have 400 healthy potato plants.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.94,0:41:37.92,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我小心地把它们挖出来以免伤到植株\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I dug them up being careful to leave their plants alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.95,0:41:42.35,Chinese,,0,0,0,,小的用来播种, 大的成了我的盘中餐\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}The smaller ones are reseed, the larger ones are my food supply.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.38,0:41:46.07,Chinese,,0,0,0,,纯天然、有机、火星培育土豆\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}All natural, organic, Martian grown potatoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.10,0:41:48.43,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你可不是天天能见到的, 不是么?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}You don't hear that everyday, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.05,0:41:50.83,Chinese,,0,0,0,,话说, 这些都毫不重要\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}And by the way, none of this matter at all
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.85,0:41:54.62,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如果我想不出办法联系美航局的话\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}If I can't figure out a way to make contact with NASA.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.60,0:42:17.62,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我知道该做什么了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I know what I'm going to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.74,0:42:47.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,哦, 他又移动了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Oh, he's moving again.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.03,0:42:49.54,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他到底要去哪儿?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Where the hell is he going?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.57,0:42:51.96,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他13天没有新动作了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}He hasn't change course for 13 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.99,0:42:54.39,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他离阿瑞斯4号一点儿都不近\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}He's no where near the Ares 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.41,0:42:56.06,Chinese,,0,0,0,,问题是他都没有定向的路线\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Problem is he's not taking a direct route.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.10,0:43:00.51,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我是说, 他可能在试图绕过一些障碍\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I mean, he might be trying to avoid some obstacle.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.54,0:43:02.22,Chinese,,0,0,0,,什么障碍?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}What obstacle?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.25,0:43:05.83,Chinese,,0,0,0,,那可是阿西达里亚平原, 一片不毛之地除了......\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}It's Acidalia Planitia. There is nothing out there except the...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.00,0:43:09.43,Chinese,,0,0,0,,啥?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.60,0:43:14.47,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我需要地图\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I need a map.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.84,0:43:22.25,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.62,0:43:24.30,Chinese,,0,0,0,,嘿, 别闹, 哥们儿, 你干嘛呢?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Hey. Come on, man. What's are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.32,0:43:26.54,Chinese,,0,0,0,,没事, 没事, 我能借用一下吗?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}It's alright. It's alright. Can I borrow this?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.57,0:43:28.79,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好, 那么, 居住舱在哪儿?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Okay. So, where's the Hab location?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.82,0:43:31.89,Chinese,,0,0,0,,北纬31.2º, 西经28.5º\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}31.2° north, 28.5° West.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.91,0:43:34.30,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好, 那, 沃特尼在哪儿?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Okay. And, where is Watney?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.61,0:43:35.94,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这儿\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.31,0:43:40.08,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好, 好\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.25,0:43:46.30,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好了, 我知道他要去哪儿了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Okay. I know where he's going.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.32,0:43:48.31,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我要去坐飞机\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I need to get on an airplane.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.11,0:44:17.59,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你好, 请跟我来\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Hi. Please follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.65,0:44:23.22,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 你好吗, 文森特? - 布鲁斯\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- How are you, Vincent? - Bruce.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.25,0:44:24.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,航程愉快吗?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Good flight?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.92,0:44:26.29,Chinese,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.63,0:44:29.78,Chinese,,0,0,0,,在仓库里, 就在转角\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}It's in storage, just around the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.46,0:45:04.97,Chinese,,0,0,0,,文森特, 很高兴见到你\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Vincent, nice to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.00,0:45:06.02,Chinese,,0,0,0,,很高兴见到你\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Nice to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.04,0:45:08.47,Chinese,,0,0,0,,马克有多大几率能让它恢复运转?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}What are the chances of Mark to get it working again?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.50,0:45:12.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不好说, 1997年就跟我们失联了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}It's hard to say. We lost contact in 1997.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.21,0:45:14.53,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们认为是电池不行了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}We think it was battery failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.55,0:45:18.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但我要指出, 它已经比预期多坚持了3倍的时间\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}But I like to point out, it last 3 times longer than we expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.11,0:45:19.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不是要批评你们实验室的作品\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Nobody is criticizing JPL's work
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.72,0:45:21.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我只想和所有97年就在这儿的人聊一聊\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I just need to speak with everybody who was here in 97.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.73,0:45:23.81,Chinese,,0,0,0,,别急, 他们来了, 大伙儿\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Don't worry, they're here. Guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.83,0:45:27.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我想介绍一下, 文森特·卡普尔, 美航局火星任务总指挥\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I would like to introduce, Vincent Kapoor, Director of the Mars missions, NASA.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.27,0:45:29.08,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这是我们现在的队伍\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}This is our current team,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.10,0:45:31.74,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 还有原先工程的人员 - 怎么样?你好吗?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- and original project members. - How ya doing? Alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.21,0:45:48.69,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 这是那个复制品? - 就是它\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- Is this the replica? - This is her.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.71,0:45:50.58,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好, 咱们看看\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Okay. Let's see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.54,0:45:53.54,Chinese,,0,0,0,,探路者\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Pathfinder.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.51,0:46:00.32,Chinese,,0,0,0,,探路者\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Pathfinder.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.74,0:47:12.94,Chinese,,0,0,0,,拜托, 拜托\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Come on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.55,0:47:36.06,Chinese,,0,0,0,,日了狗了, 好吧\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Holy shit. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.25,0:47:39.80,Chinese,,0,0,0,,无线电状态, 正在采集遥测信号\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Broadcasting Status. Listening for telemetry signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.79,0:47:43.91,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好吧, 收到信号\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Okay. Signal acquired.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.57,0:47:46.02,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 好啊 - 好吧\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- Alright. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.04,0:47:47.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,摄像头\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.41,0:48:38.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,来了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Incoming.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.23,0:48:43.31,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你收到了吗?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Are you receiving me?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.79,0:48:46.93,Chinese,,0,0,0,,是, 否\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Yes. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.70,0:48:50.22,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好, 让摄像头指向“是”\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Okay. Point the camera, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.24,0:48:52.66,Chinese,,0,0,0,,消息来回要32分钟\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}32 minutes round trip communication time.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.69,0:48:54.35,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他只能问是不是的问题\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}All he can do is ask, yes, no, questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.37,0:48:55.96,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们只能转摄像头\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}All we can do is to point the camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.99,0:48:59.08,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这可能不会像咱们围坐一桌对答如流那样\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}This won't be exactly what we might have gone, when we're around the table and snap your repartee
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.11,0:49:00.77,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 你在逗我吗? - 蒂姆, 蒂姆\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- Are you kidding me? - Tim. Tim.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.79,0:49:03.31,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 转摄像头别废话 - 收到\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- Just point the camera. - Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.34,0:49:05.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,转动摄像头\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Pointing the camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.20,0:49:21.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,是!\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.84,0:49:24.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,是!\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.18,0:49:27.39,Chinese,,0,0,0,,那么, 问题就是\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}So, here's the rub.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.41,0:49:32.87,Chinese,,0,0,0,,有时候, 我们总要进行复杂的天体物理工程学交流\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Somehow, we have to have complex astrophysical engineering conversations .
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.90,0:49:39.15,Chinese,,0,0,0,,只能通过一个静止画面摄像头, 还是1996年产的\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Using nothing but a still frame camera, from 1996.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.67,0:49:43.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好在\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Luckily
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.80,0:49:47.19,Chinese,,0,0,0,,摄像头会转\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}The camera does spin.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.22,0:49:49.55,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以, 我可以做个字母表\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}So, I can make an alphabet.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.76,0:49:51.59,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不能是我们的字母表\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}It can't be our alphabet.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.62,0:49:56.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,26个字母加上问题牌子除360度, 每个就13度角\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}26 characters plus a question card and a 360 gives us 13 degrees of arc.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.52,0:50:00.91,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这太窄了, 我永远也没法知道摄像头在指哪个\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}That's way too narrow. I'll never know where the camera is pointing at.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.09,0:50:15.15,Chinese,,0,0,0,,十六进制\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Hexadecimal.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.74,0:50:20.79,Chinese,,0,0,0,,十六进制带我飞\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Hexadecimal to the rescue.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.82,0:50:24.67,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我记得你们其中一位老是把一张ASCII表到处乱丢\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I figured one of you guys who kept an ASCII table lying around,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.69,0:50:25.91,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我是对的\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.93,0:50:30.32,Chinese,,0,0,0,,女士们先生们, 请看超级程序猿, 贝斯·约翰森\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Ladies and Gentlemen, I give you Super nerd, Beth Johanssen.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.34,0:50:33.44,Chinese,,0,0,0,,她还有《魔域2》\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Who also have copies of Zork II
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.44,0:50:37.39,Chinese,,0,0,0,,还有《火卫一的皮衣女神》, 就在她笔记本电脑上\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}and Leather Goddesses of Phobos on her personal laptop.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.73,0:50:39.12,Chinese,,0,0,0,,认真的, 约翰森\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Seriously, Johanssen.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.12,0:50:42.08,Chinese,,0,0,0,,谁想到弄这么个“孤独博物馆”的, 队长你吗?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Who thought the smithsonian of loneliness, captain ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.11,0:50:43.35,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我不是发牢骚\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Not that I'm complaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.38,0:50:46.44,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好!我又凭什么谈孤独呢?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Yes! Who am I to talk about loneliness?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.30,0:51:09.03,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我知道他这是干嘛\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I know where he's going with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.09,0:51:12.43,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Alright
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.69,0:51:58.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,FO\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}F, O.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.98,0:52:01.48,Chinese,,0,0,0,,7W\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}7, W.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.95,0:52:20.73,Chinese,,0,0,0,,文森特, 文森特\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Vincent. Vincent.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.75,0:52:22.26,Chinese,,0,0,0,,醒醒\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.71,0:52:36.39,Chinese,,0,0,0,,现在我们可以进行更复杂的对话了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Now that we can have more complicated conversations,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.42,0:52:40.41,Chinese,,0,0,0,,美航局的那群聪明人给我发过黑掉火星车的教程\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}The smart people at NASA have sent me instructions on how to hack a Rover
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.43,0:52:42.96,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这样它就能跟探路者对话\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}so that it can talk to Pathfinder.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.98,0:52:45.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如果我把它黑了, 就一小段代码, 只需修改20下\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}If I hack, a tiny bit of code, just 20 instructions
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.87,0:52:47.56,Chinese,,0,0,0,,火星车的操作系统\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}in the Rover's operating system,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.59,0:52:52.01,Chinese,,0,0,0,,美航局就能把火星车连在探路者的无线电频率上\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}NASA can link the Rover to Pathfinder's broadcasting frequency
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.04,0:52:54.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们就能运作起来\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}and we're in business.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.11,0:53:09.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,马克\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Mark,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.27,0:53:11.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我是文森特·卡普尔\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}this is Vincent Kapoor.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.60,0:53:15.53,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们从第54太阳日就开始关注你\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}We've been watching you since SOL54.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.13,0:53:19.19,Chinese,,0,0,0,,整个世界都在支持着你\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}The whole world is rooting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.30,0:53:22.93,Chinese,,0,0,0,,找探路者这招干得漂亮\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Amazing job, getting Pathfinder.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.96,0:53:25.38,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们在努力制订救援计划\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}We're working on rescue plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.41,0:53:28.56,Chinese,,0,0,0,,同时, 我们在筹备一个补给任务\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Meantime, we're putting together a supply mission
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.59,0:53:34.47,Chinese,,0,0,0,,保证你吃饱穿暖, 直到阿瑞斯4号到达\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}to keep you fed until Ares 4 arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.18,0:53:56.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,喜接来函\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Glad to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.26,0:54:02.63,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.65,0:54:06.61,Chinese,,0,0,0,,喜接来函很期待能活下去\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Glad to hear it. Really looking forward to not dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.95,0:54:08.52,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 哦 - 嚄\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- Oh. - Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.55,0:54:10.06,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好啊\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.78,0:54:18.98,Chinese,,0,0,0,,小队怎样了?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}How's the crew?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.01,0:54:22.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他们得知我还活着时说了什么?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}What did they say when they found out I was alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.14,0:54:45.48,Chinese,,0,0,0,,大伙儿, 我们能单独待会儿吗, 拜托\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Guys, can we get some space, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.95,0:54:48.03,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 我? - 对, 你\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- Me? - Yeah, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.06,0:54:50.06,Chinese,,0,0,0,,就给我一点时间\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Just give me a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.95,0:54:57.71,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你该告诉他\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}You should tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.14,0:55:12.97,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们还没告诉小队你还活着\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}We haven't told the crew you are alive yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.45,0:55:18.51,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们得让他们专心在任务上\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}We need them to concentrate on the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.52,0:55:28.82,Chinese,,0,0,0,,啥?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}(What?)
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.78,0:55:32.73,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我操!\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}(What the fuck!)
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.85,0:55:35.87,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我了个大操!\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}(What the fuck!)
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.20,0:55:43.60,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他说\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}He says.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.63,0:55:45.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他们不知道我活着?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}They don't know I'm alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.11,0:55:46.89,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我了个大和谐\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}What the F word.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.92,0:55:50.81,Chinese,,0,0,0,,和谐ing, 再和谐, 你们什么毛病?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}F word in gerund form. F word again, what's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.39,0:55:56.17,Chinese,,0,0,0,,马克, 请注意用辞\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Mark, please watch your language.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.17,0:56:03.05,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你输入的所有内容都在全球直播\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Everything you type is being broadcast live all over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.14,0:56:06.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,是嘛?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.52,0:56:16.47,Chinese,,0,0,0,,哦, 天了噜\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.14,0:56:21.67,Chinese,,0,0,0,,是的, 先生, 他现在极其紧张\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Yes, sir. He's under a tremendous amount of stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.86,0:56:24.77,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我明白, 我们在努力\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I understand. We're working on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.80,0:56:26.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我肯定他不是他说的话的意思\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I'm sure he didn't mean what he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.78,0:56:28.85,Chinese,,0,0,0,,谢谢您, 总统先生\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Thank you, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.28,0:56:31.65,Chinese,,0,0,0,,问题是, 马克说得对\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Problem is, Mark's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.66,0:56:34.12,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们越是拖着, 事态就越严重\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}The longer we wait, The worse it's going to get.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.12,0:56:35.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们得告诉小队\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}We need to tell the crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.50,0:56:38.07,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你要在文森特人在帕萨迪纳的时候提出来\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}You're bringing this up while Vincent is in Pasadena
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.10,0:56:39.57,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这样他在那边也没法跟你撕逼\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}so he can't argue the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.60,0:56:41.58,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我才不必理会文森特\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I shouldn't have to answer to Vincent.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.61,0:56:43.46,Chinese,,0,0,0,,或者别的任何人\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Or anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.27,0:56:47.25,Chinese,,0,0,0,,是时候了, 泰迪\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}It's time, Teddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.83,0:57:12.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,路易斯指挥官?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Commander Lewis?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.52,0:57:14.22,Chinese,,0,0,0,,说\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.51,0:57:16.99,Chinese,,0,0,0,,数据转移差不多完成了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Data dump is almost complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.01,0:57:19.45,Chinese,,0,0,0,,收到, 我来了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Copy that. On my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.10,0:57:33.54,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你挺忙啊\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}You're in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.57,0:57:36.94,Chinese,,0,0,0,,是啊, 我儿子昨天3岁了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Yeah. My son turned 3 yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.94,0:57:39.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,应该是聚会的照片\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Should be pictures of the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.55,0:57:54.54,Chinese,,0,0,0,,收到一堆私人信息, 正在发到你的笔记本电脑上\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Got a batch of personals. Dispatching them to your laptop now.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.56,0:57:58.14,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我可不想看, 沃格尔, 诡异的德国迷信电子邮件\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I don't mean to read, Vogel, weird German fetish e- mails.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.16,0:57:59.69,Chinese,,0,0,0,,遥测信息更新了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}The telemetry updates.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.72,0:58:01.62,Chinese,,0,0,0,,嘿, 不管是啥都是发给你的, 大哥\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Hey, whatever does it for you, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.78,0:58:06.54,Chinese,,0,0,0,,哦, 有个视频信息是, 是发给全队的\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Oh, there's a video message. It's- It's address to the whole crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.57,0:58:09.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,播放来一下, 各位\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Play it. Come on, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.03,0:58:11.97,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我来掺合一下遥测活动\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I want to get in on that telemetry action.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.68,0:58:18.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,嗨, 你们好, 我是米契, 米契·亨德逊\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Hi, hello. It's Mitch, Mitch Henderson.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.18,0:58:20.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我有一些消息\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I have some news.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.11,0:58:23.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这是没法卖关子的\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}There's no subtle way to put this.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.40,0:58:25.26,Chinese,,0,0,0,,马克·沃特尼还活着\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Mark Watney is still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.28,0:58:27.11,Chinese,,0,0,0,,哦天哪\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Oh my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.54,0:58:31.46,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我知道这是个惊喜, 我知道你们会有很多疑问\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I know that's a surprise, I know you'll have lots of questions,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.48,0:58:33.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不过, 下面是些基本情况\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}But here are the basics.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.21,0:58:36.88,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他活着, 而且健康\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}He's alive and he's healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.91,0:58:41.87,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们......我们2个月前发现的......决定不告诉你们\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}We... We found out 2 months ago and... decided not to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.90,0:58:42.99,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 什么? - 2个月?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- What? - 2 months?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.02,0:58:44.10,Chinese,,0,0,0,,哦天哪\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Oh my god.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.12,0:58:46.47,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我当时强烈反对那个决定\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I was strongly against that decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.49,0:58:49.42,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们现在告诉你们, 是因为......\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}We are telling you now, because...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.45,0:58:52.14,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们终于跟他取得联系\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}we finally have communication with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.17,0:58:54.89,Chinese,,0,0,0,,也有了可行的救援方案\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}and a viable rescue plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.24,0:58:59.08,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们会给你们发一篇关于所发生的事的报告, 完整全面的报告\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}We'll get you a write up of what happened. A full write up of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.11,0:59:00.77,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但不是你们的错\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}But it's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.80,0:59:04.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,马克每次发消息都会强调这一点\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Mark stresses that everytime it comes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.61,0:59:07.38,Chinese,,0,0,0,,那么......是啊\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}So... Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.96,0:59:11.54,Chinese,,0,0,0,,花点时间消化一下\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Take some time to absorb this.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.57,0:59:16.13,Chinese,,0,0,0,,并且......把所有想问的都发过来, 我们会回答\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}And... send all the questions you want, we'll answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.16,0:59:18.97,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好了, 亨德逊挂断\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Alright, Henderson out.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.00,0:59:21.21,Chinese,,0,0,0,,卧槽, 他活着\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Holy shit. He's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.71,0:59:22.87,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我把他丢下了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I left him behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.89,0:59:23.99,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 不 - 不\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- No. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.01,0:59:25.93,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们都把他丢下了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}We all left together.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.95,0:59:28.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你们是在听从命令\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}You were following orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.41,0:59:33.58,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我把他丢下了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I left him behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.87,0:59:45.99,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以, 现在美航局可以跟我对话, 他们不会住嘴\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}So, now that NASA can talk to me, they won't shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.02,0:59:48.98,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他们想给居住舱的每个系统都不停升级\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}They want constant updates on every Hab system,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.00,0:59:52.88,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他们还有满满一屋子人尽可能微观管理我的庄稼\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}and they've a room full of people trying to micromanage my crops.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.90,0:59:54.99,Chinese,,0,0,0,,可真是棒啊\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Which is awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.05,0:59:57.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,听着, 我是说, 我不是想表现得自大什么的\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Look, I mean, I don't mean to sound arrogant or anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.18,1:00:02.83,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但我可是这个星球上最伟大的植物学家, 所以......\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}But I am the greatest botanist on this planet, so...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.46,1:00:06.77,Chinese,,0,0,0,,哦, 跟美航局对话的又一个大好处\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Oh, one big bonus to this communication with NASA again
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.79,1:00:08.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,就是电邮, 我又能收到了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}is the e- mail, I'm getting them again.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.30,1:00:10.93,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好大一次数据转移, 就像我在赫尔墨斯号上一样\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}A big data dump. It's like when I was on the Hermes.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.95,1:00:12.73,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我甚至收到了总统的一封\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I even got one from the President.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.76,1:00:15.41,Chinese,,0,0,0,,现在最酷的是, 我收到最酷的一封是\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}The coolest one now. The coolest one I got
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.41,1:00:18.52,Chinese,,0,0,0,,来自芝加哥大学的, 我的母校\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}was from the University of Chicago, where I Alma mater.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.55,1:00:21.22,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他们说, 一旦你在一个地方种植作物\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}They said that, once you grow crops somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.24,1:00:23.96,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你就正式地“殖民”了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}You officially "colonized" it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.96,1:00:26.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以, 技术上讲\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}So, technically,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.38,1:00:29.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我殖民火星了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I colonized Mars.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.61,1:00:36.32,Chinese,,0,0,0,,来战啊, 尼尔·阿姆斯特朗\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}In your face, Neil Armstrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.32,1:00:38.42,Chinese,,0,0,0,,哦, 还有一个事儿, 有人请求\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Oh, another news. There's been a request
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.45,1:00:42.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我下次传消息的时候发一张照片\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}for me to post for a photograph on my next transmission.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.17,1:00:47.54,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我在苦苦思索我应该摆成高中生\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I am trying to figure out whether I should go with high school senior,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.57,1:00:50.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,还是婀娜纯洁少女\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}or coquettish ingenue.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.89,1:00:55.94,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不过, 我不太确定穿上宇航服是什么样\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}But, I'm not really sure how it's going to look with my spacesuit on.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.49,1:01:23.56,Chinese,,0,0,0,,噫\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Ayeee.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.17,1:01:26.47,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他在干嘛?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}What's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.49,1:01:29.06,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我要的是照片, 这啥, 他在学方兹吗?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I ask for a photo, and what, he's the Fonz?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.09,1:01:30.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,只要感谢我们好歹给了你几张, 安妮\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Just be grateful we got you something, Annie.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.96,1:01:32.92,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我不能用这个, 文森特, 你知道的\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I can't use this, Vincent, and you know that.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.94,1:01:34.52,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我需要他的脸的照片\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I need a picture of his face.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.55,1:01:35.99,Chinese,,0,0,0,,嗯, 我可以告诉他把头罩摘下来\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Well, I can tell him to take off his helmet,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.01,1:01:38.13,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是接下来他…你懂的, 就挂了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}But then he, you know, die.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.15,1:01:39.31,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}So.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.33,1:01:41.98,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们会发布照片, 并详细描述救援程序\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}We'll release the photo and we'll detail the rescue operation.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.00,1:01:45.04,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我想宣布, 我们明年会发一些补给过去\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I want to announce we're launching some supplies to him next year
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.06,1:01:47.10,Chinese,,0,0,0,,通过霍曼转移窗口\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}during the Hohmann Transfer Window.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.12,1:01:49.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,布鲁斯, 你的队伍能赶上进度吗?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Bruce, your team still on schedule?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.18,1:01:51.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,会很紧张, 不过我们能完成\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}It will be tight, but we'll make it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.42,1:01:55.81,Chinese,,0,0,0,,9个月的行程, 也就是飞船会在第868太阳日到达火星\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}9 months travel time, that puts the probe to Mars on Sol 868.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.84,1:01:57.61,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们拿到植物学队伍的分析了吗?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Did we get the Botany team's analysis?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.63,1:02:01.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,是的, 他们估计马克的作物能坚持到第912太阳日\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Yeah. They estimate Mark's crops will last till Sol 912.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.26,1:02:04.02,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他们委婉地承认了他, 他做得很不错\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}They grudgingly admit that he's- he's doing a great work.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.05,1:02:05.13,Chinese,,0,0,0,,委婉地?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Grudgingly?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.13,1:02:07.35,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这个, 是啊, 马克意图告诉他们和他们自己啪啪啪\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Well, yeah. Mark has the tendency to tell them to have sex with themselves
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.37,1:02:09.60,Chinese,,0,0,0,,只要每次他们质疑他的决定\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}whenever they question one of his decisions.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.62,1:02:12.71,Chinese,,0,0,0,,让他上线, 文森特, 我们再也受不了错误的沟通了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Get him online, Vincent. We can't afford any miscommunication.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.74,1:02:13.97,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我讨厌这样间不容发\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I hate this margin.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.99,1:02:18.38,Chinese,,0,0,0,,912太阳日的食物, 我们在第868日到达\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}912 Sols worth of food, we get there in 868.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.67,1:02:21.35,Chinese,,0,0,0,,还是在万无一失的前提下\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}That's assuming nothing goes wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.45,1:02:52.71,Chinese,,0,0,0,,啊!\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Aw!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.97,1:02:54.41,Chinese,,0,0,0,,呃啊!\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Aww!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.60,1:03:09.19,Chinese,,0,0,0,,检测到宇航服破损\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}SUIT BREACH DETECTED
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.79,1:03:19.68,Chinese,,0,0,0,,氧气浓度：极低\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}OXYGEN LEVEL CRITICAL
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.89,1:03:35.98,Chinese,,0,0,0,,氧气浓度：10%\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}OXYGEN LEVEL : 10%
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.21,1:03:53.29,Chinese,,0,0,0,,氧气浓度：5%\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}OXYGEN LEVEL : 5%
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.29,1:04:05.10,Chinese,,0,0,0,,宇航服压力：稳定\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}SUIT PRESSURE STABLE
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.90,1:06:02.22,Chinese,,0,0,0,,压力：稳定\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}PRESSURE STABLE
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.52,1:06:36.56,Chinese,,0,0,0,,完了!\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}GONE!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.58,1:06:39.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,完了, 完了, 完了, 完了!\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Gone, gone, gone, gone!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.40,1:06:59.34,Chinese,,0,0,0,,作物都死了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Crops are dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.36,1:07:01.65,Chinese,,0,0,0,,完全失压, 大部分水都沸腾掉了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Complete loss of pressure boiled off most of the water.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.68,1:07:04.86,Chinese,,0,0,0,,之前活下来的细菌都在零下温度中死掉了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Any bacteria that survived died in the subzero temperatures
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.89,1:07:06.96,Chinese,,0,0,0,,暴露在火星的大气里就会这样\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}when exposed to Mar's atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.96,1:07:09.03,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他有多长时间?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}How long has he have?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.96,1:07:14.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,哦, 他还可以吃现有的土豆, 只不过不能再种了, 所以......\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Oh. He can still eat the potatoes he has, he just can't grow anymore, so...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.14,1:07:16.99,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他有......200太阳日\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Give him... 200 Sols.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.02,1:07:20.68,Chinese,,0,0,0,,太空餐能吃多久?409太阳日?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Rations give him to what? Sol 409?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.71,1:07:22.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,对, 加上土豆, 609日\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}So, with potatoes, 609.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.90,1:07:25.69,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以, 到第868太阳日, 他都死透了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}So, by Sol 868, he'll be long dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.69,1:07:27.73,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们只能尽快发射\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}We're going to have to launch as soon as possible,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.76,1:07:30.34,Chinese,,0,0,0,,来改变航程时间\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}which changes our travel time.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.60,1:07:32.65,Chinese,,0,0,0,,是的, 我们正在研究\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Yeah, we're working on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.17,1:07:37.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,初步估计需要414天的航程\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Preliminary estimates call for a 414 day trip.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.70,1:07:39.99,Chinese,,0,0,0,,现在是第135太阳日\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}It's Sol 135 now.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.99,1:07:43.48,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们需要13天来搭建助推器, 进行检查\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}We need 13 days to mount the boosters, perform inspections
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.50,1:07:46.93,Chinese,,0,0,0,,也就是布鲁斯和他的团队\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}which gives Bruce and his team
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.96,1:07:50.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,有47天来做飞行器\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}47 days to make this probe.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.62,1:07:54.13,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我会让你和布鲁斯通话, 把消息告诉他\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I'll let you call Bruce. Give him the news.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.04,1:07:58.64,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.02,1:08:04.34,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我......我得去换一下衣服\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I'm...  I'm going to need a change of clothes.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.41,1:08:14.41,Chinese,,0,0,0,,亲爱的马克\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Dear Mark,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.81,1:08:19.91,Chinese,,0,0,0,,显然, 美航局现在允许我们和你对话了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Apparently, NASA's letting us talk to you now.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.68,1:08:24.66,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而我, 抽到了下下签\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}And I, drew the short straw.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.92,1:08:32.04,Chinese,,0,0,0,,抱歉我们把你扔在了火星\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Sorry we left you behind on Mars,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.06,1:08:35.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是我们就是不喜欢你\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}but we just don't like you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.69,1:08:42.49,Chinese,,0,0,0,,还有, 赫尔墨斯号少了你之后宽敞多了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Also, it's a lot roomier on the Hermes without you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.52,1:08:46.45,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们得轮流做你的工作\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}We have to take turns doing your tasks,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.48,1:08:50.66,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不过, 我是说, 就是种地嘛\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}but, I mean, it's only botany.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.30,1:08:52.44,Chinese,,0,0,0,,算不上是科学\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}It's not real science.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.47,1:08:54.47,Chinese,,0,0,0,,哦, 天哪\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Oh, Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.77,1:08:57.78,Chinese,,0,0,0,,火星怎么样?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}How's Mars?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.62,1:09:06.14,Chinese,,0,0,0,,亲爱的马丁内斯, 火星挺好\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Dear Martinez, Mars is fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.16,1:09:09.10,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我不小心把居住舱给炸了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I accidentally blew up the Hab,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.12,1:09:16.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但不幸的是, 路易斯指挥官所有的迪斯科音乐都逃过一劫\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}but unfortunately all of Commander Lewis' disco music still survived.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.38,1:09:20.94,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但不幸的是, 路易斯指挥官所有的迪斯科音乐都逃过一劫\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}but unfortunately all of Commander Lewis' disco music still survived.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.17,1:09:26.41,Chinese,,0,0,0,,每天我都出去走走, 看看广袤的地平线\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Every day I go outside and look at the vast horizons.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.44,1:09:30.31,Chinese,,0,0,0,,每天我都出去走走, 看看广袤的地平线\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Every day I go outside and look at the vast horizons.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.33,1:09:32.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,只是因为我可以\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Just because I can.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.31,1:09:34.77,Chinese,,0,0,0,,只是因为我可以\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Just because I can.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.79,1:09:38.86,Chinese,,0,0,0,,代我向其他人问好\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Tell the others I said hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.64,1:09:42.46,Chinese,,0,0,0,,会的, 哥们儿\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Will do, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.11,1:11:14.25,Chinese,,0,0,0,,压力：稳定\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}PRESSURE STABLE.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.85,1:11:56.31,Chinese,,0,0,0,,5, 10\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}5, 10,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.33,1:11:59.85,Chinese,,0,0,0,,15, 20, 30, 35\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}15, 20, 30, 35,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.63,1:12:02.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,40\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}40.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.62,1:12:04.46,Chinese,,0,0,0,,52\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}52.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.63,1:12:34.10,Chinese,,0,0,0,,里奇\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Rich.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.17,1:12:36.34,Chinese,,0,0,0,,里奇\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Rich.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.36,1:12:37.61,Chinese,,0,0,0,,醒醒\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Wake up.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.92,1:12:42.29,Chinese,,0,0,0,,抱歉, 但他们在问飞行器的情况\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Sorry, but they're asking for the probe courses.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.31,1:12:43.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,几点了?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}What time is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.98,1:12:46.53,Chinese,,0,0,0,,大概......3:42\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}It's about... 03:42
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.44,1:12:53.78,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我知道情况越来越糟\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I know we're coming at this backwards,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.81,1:12:57.66,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是我们不能定下一个有太多未知因素的发射日期\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}but we can't commit to a firm launch date with so many unknowns.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.06,1:12:59.61,Chinese,,0,0,0,,还好\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.07,1:13:02.88,Chinese,,0,0,0,,全部25种发射模型都是414天到火星\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}All 25 models for launch will take 414 days to reach the Mars.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.90,1:13:04.67,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他们在推进时间上差别很小\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}They varies slightly in thrust duration and
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.69,1:13:07.30,Chinese,,0,0,0,,燃料消耗也几乎相等\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}fuel requirement is nearly as identical.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.78,1:13:09.78,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不是很好的发射时间, 是吧?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Not a good time to launch, is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.78,1:13:12.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,是啊, 地球和火星的位置真的很不利\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Yeah. Earth and Mars are really badly positioned.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.98,1:13:15.60,Chinese,,0,0,0,,真是, 差点儿就能更容易, 只要......\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Heck, it'd almost be easier if you...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.65,1:13:19.65,Chinese,,0,0,0,,差点儿就能更容易什么?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Almost easier to what?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.24,1:13:22.15,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我要再喝点咖啡\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I need more coffee.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.70,1:13:26.33,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 你没事吧? - 没事\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- Are you alright? - It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.49,1:13:32.67,Chinese,,0,0,0,,差点儿就能更容易啥啊?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Almost easier to what?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.48,1:13:46.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你知道我是你上司, 是吧?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}You do understand I'm your boss, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.44,1:13:47.88,Chinese,,0,0,0,,嗯哼\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Uh- huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.49,1:13:55.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们来问个非常非常昂贵的问题\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Let's ask the very very expensive question.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.54,1:13:57.23,Chinese,,0,0,0,,飞行器能按时就绪吗?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Is the probe going to be ready on time?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.25,1:13:59.26,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 我们落后了 - 给我个数字\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- We are behind. - Give me a number.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.28,1:14:02.32,Chinese,,0,0,0,,15天, 15天我就能完成\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}15 days. 15 days and I can get it done.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.35,1:14:05.71,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好, 就定下15天13天的时候搭建飞行器\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Alright, let's create 15 days. 13 days to mount the probe.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.72,1:14:07.05,Chinese,,0,0,0,,可以提前吗?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Can we reduce?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.07,1:14:09.42,Chinese,,0,0,0,,其实搭建飞行器要3天\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}It actually takes 3 days to mount the probe.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.42,1:14:11.37,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但我们可以压缩到2天, 是吧?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}And we can get it down to 2, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.39,1:14:12.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我可以压缩到2天\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I can get it down to 2.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.98,1:14:14.80,Chinese,,0,0,0,,10天的时间用来检查和测试\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}10 days are for tests and inspections.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.83,1:14:17.93,Chinese,,0,0,0,,十次检查有几次能发现问题?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}How often do those inspections reveal a problem?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.05,1:14:20.22,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你的意思是我们不检查了?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Are you suggesting we don't do the inspections?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.24,1:14:22.71,Chinese,,0,0,0,,现在, 我问的是十次检查有几次能发现问题?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Right now, I'm asking how often they reveal a problem?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.74,1:14:23.94,Chinese,,0,0,0,,半次\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}1 in 20.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.96,1:14:25.63,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但检查正是倒计时会中止的原因\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}But that's grounds for countdown halt.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.65,1:14:26.86,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们不能冒这个险\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}We can't take that chance.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.86,1:14:30.11,Chinese,,0,0,0,,还有谁有更安全的方法来争取更多时间吗?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Anyone else know a safer way to buy more time?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.68,1:14:36.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,凯勒博士, 让沃特尼节衣缩食多挺4天\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Dr. Keller, stretch Watney's rations 4 more days.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.12,1:14:38.21,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他不会乐意, 但我们就可以凑出15天\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}He's not going to like it, but that will get us to 15.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.25,1:14:40.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 而且我们要取消检查 - 泰迪\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- And we'll cancel the inspections. - Teddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.23,1:14:42.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 长官, 一旦出了事儿 - 责任在我\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- Sir, If that ever got out. - It's on me.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.43,1:14:43.79,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你们有2周时间\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}You got your 2 weeks.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.81,1:14:45.65,Chinese,,0,0,0,,把活干完!\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Get it done!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.30,1:14:50.35,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以, 现在, 我得撑到飞行器把更多食物带来\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}So, now, I have to hold out until the probe gets here with more food.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.38,1:14:53.01,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你想看看最低卡路里是什么概念吗?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}You want to see what minimum calorie count looks like?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.01,1:14:54.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,标准节食方案\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Standard issue ration.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.72,1:14:58.78,Chinese,,0,0,0,,现在不是每1天吃3个\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}But instead of 3 of these every 1 day,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.81,1:15:03.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而是每3天吃1个\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I'm now eating 1 of these every 3 days.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.06,1:15:06.52,Chinese,,0,0,0,,现在他们要求我......\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}And now they've asked me...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.97,1:15:08.56,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这么做\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}to do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.91,1:15:14.56,Chinese,,0,0,0,,问题是\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}The point is,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.53,1:15:18.83,Chinese,,0,0,0,,多节食4天\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}stretch the rations 4 more days.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.57,1:15:21.86,Chinese,,0,0,0,,真是蛋疼\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}These are real dick punch.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.35,1:15:24.98,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我......\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I'm...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.23,1:15:28.63,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我要用这个土豆蘸维生素片吃\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I'm going to dip this potato in some crashed vitacarn.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.75,1:15:32.68,Chinese,,0,0,0,,谁也拦不了我\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}And there's nobody who can stop me.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.23,1:15:45.88,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我已经7天没有番茄酱了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}It has been 7 days since I ran out of ketchup.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.43,1:15:59.44,Chinese,,0,0,0,,抬, 抬, 抬\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Up. Up, up.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.16,1:16:01.78,Chinese,,0,0,0,,放这儿\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Come up here.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.67,1:16:11.71,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我是航行指挥员, 马上开始检查发射状态\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}This is the Flight Director. Soon begin launch status check.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.71,1:16:14.47,Chinese,,0,0,0,,收到, 指挥开始检查发射状态\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Roger that, Flight. Beginning launch status check.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.47,1:16:16.73,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你信上帝吗, 文森特?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Do you believe in god, Vincent?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.87,1:16:19.35,Chinese,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.88,1:16:24.10,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这个, 我爸在印度的时候, 我妈是个施洗者, 所以, 是啊\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Well. My father was a Hindu, My mother's a Baptist, so, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.13,1:16:26.19,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我信好几个神\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I believe in several.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.36,1:16:30.31,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们会接受任何援手\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}We'll take all the help we can get.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.31,1:16:32.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,发射状态检查完毕\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Launch status check complete.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.30,1:16:33.82,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我是指挥\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}This is Flight.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.82,1:16:35.49,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们准备发射\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}We are go for launch.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.49,1:16:36.63,Chinese,,0,0,0,,开始倒计时\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Proceed with the count.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.66,1:16:37.74,Chinese,,0,0,0,,10\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}10.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.77,1:16:39.61,Chinese,,0,0,0,,9, 8\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}9, 8,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.61,1:16:41.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,7, 6\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}7, 6,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.19,1:16:42.67,Chinese,,0,0,0,,主引擎启动\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Main engines start.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:42.67,1:16:44.64,Chinese,,0,0,0,,4, 3\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}4, 3,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.67,1:16:45.68,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 2 - 点火\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- 2, - Ignition.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.71,1:16:47.08,Chinese,,0,0,0,,1\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}1.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.92,1:16:49.88,Chinese,,0,0,0,,发射\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Liftoff.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.60,1:16:53.45,Chinese,,0,0,0,,推进成功\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Good thrust.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.97,1:16:59.19,Chinese,,0,0,0,,状态正常\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Performance is normal.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.14,1:17:14.41,Chinese,,0,0,0,,火箭反馈数据正常\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}The payload is giving good data.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.43,1:17:18.67,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它现在安若磐石, 指挥推力矢量控制表现正常\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}She's rock solid at this point, Flight. TVC looks good.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.69,1:17:20.44,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 天啊 - 好!\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- My god. - Yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.46,1:17:22.89,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 哟呼! - 耶\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- Yoo hoo! - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.23,1:17:30.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,交通数据收集系统还要再工作一段时间\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}We have an extra TDCS duration.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.22,1:17:32.48,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好像有点异常振动, 指挥\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}We're getting a little shimmy, Flight.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.77,1:17:34.32,Chinese,,0,0,0,,再说一遍?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Say again?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.45,1:17:36.82,Chinese,,0,0,0,,火箭发生了剧烈的进动\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}We're getting a very large precession.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.84,1:17:38.48,Chinese,,0,0,0,,还好不?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Are we good?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.13,1:17:40.67,Chinese,,0,0,0,,指挥, 到临界值了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Flight, it's hitting the red line.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.70,1:17:44.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,绕长轴17º的进动\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Spinning on the long axis with a 17° precession.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.73,1:17:46.43,Chinese,,0,0,0,,发射指挥, 什么情况?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Launch, what's happening?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.45,1:17:48.53,Chinese,,0,0,0,,伊里斯受力为7个重力\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Force on Iris is at 7 g's.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.56,1:17:50.88,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们已经没有飞行器的读数了, 指挥\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}We've lost the readings on the probe, Flight.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.10,1:17:54.01,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 哦 - 哦!\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- Oh. - Oh!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.04,1:17:57.21,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 哦, 天哪 - 天哪\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- Oh, Jesus Christ. - Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.16,1:18:02.08,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它解体了, 指挥\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}We lost it, Flight.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.51,1:18:06.73,Chinese,,0,0,0,,卫星通讯?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}SatCom?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.76,1:18:09.49,Chinese,,0,0,0,,没有卫星接收到信号\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}No satellite acquisition of signal.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.70,1:18:13.03,Chinese,,0,0,0,,失联\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}LOS.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.05,1:18:14.30,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这儿也失联了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}LOS here too.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.33,1:18:18.10,Chinese,,0,0,0,,美国驱逐舰, 斯托克顿, 报告有碎片从天而落\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}US Destroyer, Stockton, Reporting debris falling from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.12,1:18:20.73,Chinese,,0,0,0,,发射控制中心所有人保持原位\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Everyone in the LCC maintain your positions.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.75,1:18:23.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,地面控制中心, 锁上门\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}GC. Lock the doors.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.62,1:18:53.67,Chinese,,0,0,0,,路易斯指挥官\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Commander Lewis,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.70,1:18:58.01,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我可能需要你为我做些事情\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I may need you to do something for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.80,1:19:04.45,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如果我死了, 我需要你去拜访一下我父母\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}If I die, I need you to check in with my parents.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.91,1:19:09.05,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他们会愿意听到我们在火星时的一切\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}They will want to hear all about our time here on Mars.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.93,1:19:11.93,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我知道这是强人所难\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I know that sucks,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.93,1:19:16.11,Chinese,,0,0,0,,很难去跟一对夫妇谈论\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}and it will be hard talking to a couple
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.13,1:19:18.92,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他们死去的儿子\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}about their dead son.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.52,1:19:21.71,Chinese,,0,0,0,,有太多要问\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}It's a lot to ask.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.00,1:19:26.63,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以我才拜托你\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Which is why I'm asking you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.11,1:19:29.07,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我没有放弃\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I'm not giving up.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.09,1:19:33.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我只是需要为每种结果做准备\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I just need to prepare for every outcome.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.85,1:19:37.85,Chinese,,0,0,0,,请告诉他们\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Please tell them.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.82,1:19:42.27,Chinese,,0,0,0,,告诉他们我爱我的工作\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Tell them I love what I do,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.03,1:19:48.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而且我真的很擅长\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}And I'm really good at it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.03,1:19:53.61,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而且我的牺牲\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}And I'm dying
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.43,1:19:57.38,Chinese,,0,0,0,,是为了大事\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}for something big
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.41,1:20:00.48,Chinese,,0,0,0,,美好的\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}and beautiful,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.42,1:20:06.46,Chinese,,0,0,0,,比我更伟大的事\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}and greater than me.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.30,1:20:11.22,Chinese,,0,0,0,,告诉他们, 我说了我能接受\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Tell them I said I can live with that.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.06,1:20:13.99,Chinese,,0,0,0,,还要告诉他们\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}And tell them,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.74,1:20:19.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,谢谢你们做我的爸爸妈妈\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}thank you for being my mom and dad.
