Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.35,1:20:32.99,Chinese,,0,0,0,,熔化了蛋白块, 导致载重不均\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}liquified the cubes and created an imbalance load.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.01,1:20:36.14,Chinese,,0,0,0,,文森特, 这不应该在检查阶段就能发现吗?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Vincent, why wasn't this address from the inspection phase?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.16,1:20:40.67,Chinese,,0,0,0,,为了赶发射窗口, 我们只得加速进程\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}In order to make our launch window, we were forced to accelerate our schedule.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.50,1:20:43.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他们的宇航员这样会饿死\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Their astronaut is going to die from hunger.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.63,1:20:47.86,Chinese,,0,0,0,,当然, 还有其他办法\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Of course. There are other ways.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.06,1:20:52.67,Chinese,,0,0,0,,太阳神的助推器, 我们的工程师检查过数据\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Our engineers have ran the numbers of the Taiyang Shen's boosters.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.70,1:20:56.29,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它的容量可以到达火星的轨道\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}It has the fuel capacity to reach Mars orbit.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.31,1:20:58.01,Chinese,,0,0,0,,美航局为什么没有找我们?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Why didn't NASA approach us?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.04,1:20:59.87,Chinese,,0,0,0,,因为他们不知道\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Because they don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.90,1:21:03.06,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们的数据是绝密的\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Our data is classified information.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.76,1:21:06.49,Chinese,,0,0,0,,也就是说\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}That's to say.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.51,1:21:08.63,Chinese,,0,0,0,,假如我们什么都不做\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}If we do nothing...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.65,1:21:13.71,Chinese,,0,0,0,,世界将永远不会知道, 其实我们是可以帮得上忙的\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}The world will never knew, actually we could have helped.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.74,1:21:16.38,Chinese,,0,0,0,,那么, 仅仅是为了论证\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}So. For the sake of argument,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.40,1:21:18.94,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如果我们决定帮助他们\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}let's say we decided to help them.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.97,1:21:23.82,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们把助推器给了他们, 也就是取消了太阳神计划\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}We give them the boosters, that means the cancellation of Taiyang Shen's program.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.13,1:21:27.51,Chinese,,0,0,0,,那我们, 就从航天的角度解决问题\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Then let us, from Aerospace point of view, try to solve this problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.53,1:21:29.49,Chinese,,0,0,0,,寻求合作\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Find a way to cooperate.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.35,1:21:33.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,是\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.73,1:21:37.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,是, 我明白\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.64,1:21:41.15,Chinese,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.53,1:21:46.05,Chinese,,0,0,0,,太好了!\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.90,1:21:48.02,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Alright!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:48.02,1:21:51.77,Chinese,,0,0,0,,多亏我在中国的叔叔汤米, 我们可以再来一发\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Thanks to my uncle Tommy in China, We got another chance at this.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.78,1:21:54.99,Chinese,,0,0,0,,现在我们用了62天完成伊里斯飞行器\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Now we finished the Iris probe in 62 days,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.99,1:21:59.15,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们如今要在28天里完成它\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}we're now going to attempt to finish it in 28.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.50,1:22:25.44,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们可以抛掉所有着陆设备\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}We can jettison any kind of landing systems.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.46,1:22:29.57,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们只送补给, 我们可以撞在火星上\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}We're sending only rations. We can crash land on Mars.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.22,1:22:31.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你应该挂掉电话\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}You should hang up the phone.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.73,1:22:33.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 抱歉, 你谁啊? - 我叫里奇·珀内尔\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- I'm sorry, who are you? - My name is Rich Purnell.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.53,1:22:37.05,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我在天文动力学部门工作, 你应该挂电话了, 就现在\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I work in Astrodynamics, and you should hang up the phone, right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.43,1:22:40.08,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好吧, 好吧\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Alright. Alright.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.27,1:22:42.05,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我回头打给你\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I'm going to call you back.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.62,1:22:44.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我知道怎么救马克·沃特尼\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I know how to save Mark Watney.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.67,1:22:48.27,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你的飞行器计划不会成功, 太多地方会出问题\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Your probe plan won't work. Too many things can go wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.29,1:22:49.52,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我有上策\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I got a better way.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.55,1:22:52.17,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 天文动力学? - 是啊\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- Astrodynamics? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.45,1:22:55.39,Chinese,,0,0,0,,爱隆计划是什么鬼?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}What the hell is Project Elrond?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.41,1:22:56.58,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我得亡羊补牢\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I had to make something up.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.58,1:22:58.43,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是, 爱隆?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}But, Elrond?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.45,1:23:00.62,Chinese,,0,0,0,,因为这是个秘密会议\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Because it's a secret meeting.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.62,1:23:03.32,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道的?为什么爱隆的意思是秘密会议?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}How do you know that? Why does Elrond mean secret meeting?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.34,1:23:06.06,Chinese,,0,0,0,,爱隆的会议, 来自《指环王》\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}The Council of Elrond. It's from the "Lord Of The Rings."
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.06,1:23:07.44,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 在那个会议上他们 - 《指环王》\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- It's the meeting where they - The Lord Of The Rings.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.46,1:23:09.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,决定毁掉魔戒\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}decide to destroy the One ring.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.50,1:23:11.34,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如果我们要称之爱隆计划\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}If we are going to call something Project Elrond,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.34,1:23:13.63,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我要我的代号叫做格洛芬德尔\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I would like my codename to be Glorfindel.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.63,1:23:15.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我讨厌你们每一个人\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I hate everyone of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.78,1:23:18.14,Chinese,,0,0,0,,泰迪到现在都还一头雾水呢\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Teddy doesn't even know about this yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.17,1:23:19.26,Chinese,,0,0,0,,抱歉, 你是谁?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I'm sorry. Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.29,1:23:22.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这是里奇·珀内尔, 天文动力学家\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}This is Rich Purnell, Astrodynamics.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.52,1:23:24.27,Chinese,,0,0,0,,把你刚才跟我说的告诉他们\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Tell them what you just told me.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.28,1:23:28.12,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我可以让赫尔墨斯号在第561太阳日前回到火星\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I can get the Hermes back to Mars by Sol 561.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.14,1:23:30.63,Chinese,,0,0,0,,怎么做?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}How?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.39,1:23:37.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,请问, 你可以帮个忙站到那里去吗?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Would you stand right there for me, please?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.65,1:23:41.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,谢谢, 就那儿, 很好\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Thanks. Right there, great.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.03,1:23:45.69,Chinese,,0,0,0,,麻烦您, 站在那儿?就那儿\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}And could you, stand right there? Right there.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.61,1:23:53.62,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好, 咱们假设这个订书机是赫尔墨斯号\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Okay. Let's pretend that this stapler is the Hermes,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.64,1:23:56.22,Chinese,,0,0,0,,您是......\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}And you are...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.22,1:23:57.60,Chinese,,0,0,0,,抱歉, 您叫什么来着?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I'm sorry. What's your name again?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.60,1:24:01.27,Chinese,,0,0,0,,泰迪, 我是美航局局长\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Teddy. I'm the director of NASA.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.31,1:24:03.57,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好, 泰迪, 你是地球\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Cool. Teddy, you're Earth.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.58,1:24:06.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,现在, 赫尔墨斯号正朝着你\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}And right now, the Hermes is heading towards you,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.02,1:24:08.65,Chinese,,0,0,0,,开始数月之久的减速被捕获之旅\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}starting it's months long deceleration intercept,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.65,1:24:12.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但反之, 我想提出的是\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}but instead, what I'm proposing is,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.20,1:24:19.30,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它现在开始加速, 保持速度, 甚至获得更多速度\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}It start accelerating immediately, to preserve velocity and gain even more.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.32,1:24:22.01,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们不被地球捕获, 但我们足够靠近\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}We don't intercept with Earth at all, but we come close enough...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.04,1:24:24.35,Chinese,,0,0,0,,以借助重力调整路线\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}to get a gravity assist and adjust course.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.38,1:24:26.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们这么做的同时\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}While we're doing that,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.42,1:24:31.42,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 我们换上新的飞行器 - 太阳神\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- we resupply with the probe. - The Taiyang Shen.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.42,1:24:33.07,Chinese,,0,0,0,,带上我们需要运送的所有补给\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Pick up whatever provisions we need.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.10,1:24:36.29,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们就加速直奔火星而去了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}And now we accelerating towards Mars.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.96,1:24:39.45,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你是火星\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}You're Mars.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.46,1:24:42.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,现在, 我们速度太快没法落入轨道, 但是......\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Now, we are going too fast at this point to fall into orbit, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.52,1:24:44.02,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们可以经过定点\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}we can do a flyby.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.02,1:24:47.14,Chinese,,0,0,0,,经过定点有什么用, 如果你没法让沃特尼离开火星表面?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}What good is a flyby if you can't get Watney off the surface?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.16,1:24:50.51,Chinese,,0,0,0,,沃特尼可以用微型飞行器拦截\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Watney would intercept using  the MAV.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.53,1:24:51.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,嗷\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Ow.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.47,1:24:56.30,Chinese,,0,0,0,,然后我们就往家走\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}And then we just head home.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.98,1:25:04.22,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我做过计算了, 没问题的\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I done the math. It checks out.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.41,1:25:06.85,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 里奇 - 在, 长官\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- Rich. - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.88,1:25:09.33,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 出去 - 好的\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- Get out. - Alright.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.32,1:25:17.32,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 他说得对吗? - 对\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- Is he right? - Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.34,1:25:19.86,Chinese,,0,0,0,,布鲁斯, 你怎么看?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Bruce, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.89,1:25:22.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这个嘛, 听文森特的\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Well, If Vincent say so.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.81,1:25:26.33,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 我们得用太阳神 - 嗯哼\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- We need to use the Taiyang Shen. - Uh- huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.35,1:25:28.43,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我, 我听漏什么了?为什么那么重要?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Wha- What am I missing? Why is that important?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.44,1:25:29.69,Chinese,,0,0,0,,因为我们要一击必中\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Because we can only do one.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.72,1:25:32.23,Chinese,,0,0,0,,给沃特尼送去足够坚持到阿瑞斯4号的食物\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Send Watney enough food to last till Ares 4,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.25,1:25:34.14,Chinese,,0,0,0,,和让赫尔墨斯号现在回去找他\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}or send Hermes back to get him right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.17,1:25:38.37,Chinese,,0,0,0,,两个计划都需要太阳神所以, 我们得二选一\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Both plans require the Taiyang Shen. So, we have to choose.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.37,1:25:40.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是, 赫尔墨斯号成员呢?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}But, what about the Hermes' crew?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.01,1:25:45.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,到时候得要求他们给他们的任务额外加上533天\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}It would be asking them, to add 533 extra days to their mission.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.00,1:25:47.42,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他们会毫不犹豫, 二话不说\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}And they wouldn't hesitate, not for a second.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.44,1:25:51.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,赫尔墨斯号能超出计划任务运行533天吗?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Can the Hermes function for 533 days beyond the scheduled mission?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.21,1:25:52.34,Chinese,,0,0,0,,应该可以\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Should.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.35,1:25:54.35,Chinese,,0,0,0,,按照完成整个阿瑞斯任务建造的\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Built to last the full Ares mission.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.38,1:25:57.06,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以, 技术上讲, 现在只走到了其寿命的一半\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}So, technically, it's only half way through it's lifespan.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.09,1:25:59.75,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 不过, 如果出了问题 - 那么, 我们就会失去整个小队\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- But, if something goes wrong. - Then, we lose the crew.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.75,1:26:03.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以怎么办?我们要么冒高风险杀死一个人, 或者\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}So, what? We, either have a high chance of killing 1 person, or
Dialogue: 0,1:26:03.97,1:26:06.47,Chinese,,0,0,0,,冒低风险杀死6个人\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}low chance of killing 6 people.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.48,1:26:08.12,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们怎么抉择?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}How do we make that decision?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.14,1:26:10.19,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们不用抉择, 布鲁斯\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}We don't have to make it, Bruce.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.22,1:26:11.29,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他来\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}He does.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.31,1:26:12.73,Chinese,,0,0,0,,是啊, 但是废话\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Yeah. But, bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.73,1:26:14.92,Chinese,,0,0,0,,应该让路易斯指挥官来决定\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Should be Commander Lewis' call.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.95,1:26:18.11,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们仍有机会带5名宇航员安然回家\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}We still have a chance to bring 5 astronauts home safe and sound.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.14,1:26:20.93,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我不想用他们的生命冒险\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I'm not risking their lives.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.95,1:26:23.51,Chinese,,0,0,0,,让他们来做决定\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Let them make that decision.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.53,1:26:27.06,Chinese,,0,0,0,,米契, 我们不会采纳你的建议\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Mitch, we're going with option 1.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.00,1:26:30.53,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你他妈就是个懦夫\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}You god damn coward.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.27,1:26:50.91,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 约翰森? - 嗯\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- Johanssen? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.93,1:26:53.61,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我知道现在是你的私人时间, 我可以打搅一下吗?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I know it's your private time. Can I bother you for a second?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.61,1:26:54.73,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好, 说吧\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Yeah, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.73,1:26:57.12,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 你在哪儿? - 健身房\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- Where are you? - The gym.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.18,1:27:19.30,Chinese,,0,0,0,,咋了?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}What's up?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.33,1:27:24.32,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我刚收到我妻子的电邮, 主题是《我们的孩子》\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I just got an e- mail from my wife, and the subject line says, "our children."
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.35,1:27:27.23,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我的电脑打不开附件\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}My computer won't open the attachment.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.80,1:27:31.12,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好吧, 咱们看看\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Okay. Let's take a look.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.75,1:27:38.59,Chinese,,0,0,0,,看看\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.66,1:27:41.93,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这不是JPEG文件\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}This isn't a jpeg.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.64,1:27:45.94,Chinese,,0,0,0,,是, 是个纯ASCII文件\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}It's a- It's a plain ASCII text file.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.87,1:27:50.68,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我不太确定这是啥, 它......\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I don't really know what we're looking at. It's...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.82,1:27:53.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你能看懂吗?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}That make any sense to you?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.42,1:27:56.75,Chinese,,0,0,0,,里奇·珀内尔演算\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Rich Purnell maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.75,1:28:00.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,是对赫尔墨斯号航线的一种演算\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}It's a course maneuver for the Hermes.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.89,1:28:04.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,天哪\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}My god.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.10,1:28:10.01,Chinese,,0,0,0,,211天之后任务就要以进入地球轨道告终了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}The mission concludes with Earth intercept 211 days later.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.30,1:28:11.88,Chinese,,0,0,0,,能奏效吗?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Would it work?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.91,1:28:13.97,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们计算过了, 能行\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}We ran the numbers. They checked out.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.00,1:28:15.83,Chinese,,0,0,0,,真是个了不得的任务\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} It's a brilliant course.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.86,1:28:18.48,Chinese,,0,0,0,,为啥搞得这么神秘?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} So, why all the cloak and dagger?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.50,1:28:20.65,Chinese,,0,0,0,,因为这是直接违抗美航局的决定的\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Because it goes directly against NASA's decision.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.65,1:28:24.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,是啊, 如果我们执行这个任务, 他们必须给我们送补给, 要不我们就饿死了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Yeah. If we do the maneuver, they have to send the supply ship or we die.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.95,1:28:28.44,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们可以强迫他们\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} We have the opportunity to force their hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.45,1:28:32.64,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我已我们怎么办?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} So, are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.14,1:28:35.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如果是我的决定, 我们现在就已经在路上了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} If it's up to me, we'll already be on our way.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.23,1:28:37.77,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但就是你的决定啊, 难不成不是么?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} But it is, no, isn't it? Up to you?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.77,1:28:39.13,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这次不是\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Not this time.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.16,1:28:42.52,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这个任务可是美航局明确反对的\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} This is something NASA expressly rejected.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.12,1:28:46.37,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这可算是反叛, 我可不愿意直接被贯于这个名号\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} We're talking about mutiny here, which is not a word that I take lightly
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.39,1:28:49.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以, 我们要么一起, 要么什么都不干\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}So, we do this together, or not at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.23,1:28:52.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,在你回答去不去之前, 想想后果\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} And, before you answer, consider the consequences.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.18,1:28:55.52,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如果我们在对接补给的时候没搞好, 我们都得死\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} If we mess up the supply rendezvous, we die.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.55,1:28:58.26,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如果我们没能好好的借助地心引力, 我们也是死\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} If we mess up the Earth gravity assist, we die.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.29,1:29:00.51,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如果我们每一环都做得完美\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} If we do everything perfectly,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.53,1:29:04.85,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们还得在原本的任务上多加533 天\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} We add 533 days to our mission.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.87,1:29:09.15,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们得在533天之后才能见到我们的家人\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} 533 more days, before we see our families again.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.17,1:29:15.29,Chinese,,0,0,0,,在计划之外的533任务, 任何事情都可能发生\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} 533 days of unplanned space travel where anything can go wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.29,1:29:19.48,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如果任务出问题, 我们都回不去家\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} If it's mission critical, we die.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.50,1:29:20.62,Chinese,,0,0,0,,算上我\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Sign me up.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.64,1:29:22.38,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好好好, 牛仔, 别急啊\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Alright, cowboy, slow down.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.38,1:29:24.12,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你我都是军人\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} You and I, we're military.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.14,1:29:26.15,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们回家以后有可能会被升职加薪\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Chances are, we go home, they'll court martial us.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.18,1:29:28.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 哦对哦, 还有这个呢 - 但对其他人来说,\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} - Oh yeah, there's that. - And for the rest of you guys,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.22,1:29:31.26,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我保证他们不会再把你们送到太空了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} I guarantee they will never send you back up here again.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.28,1:29:35.83,Chinese,,0,0,0,,棒, 如果我们执行这个任务, 怎么搞?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Good. So, if we go for it, how would it work?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.85,1:29:37.61,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我来计划一下, 然后执行\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} I'll plot the course and execute it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.64,1:29:39.02,Chinese,,0,0,0,,远程遥控\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Remote override.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.05,1:29:42.31,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他们可以在地球上的总部控制赫尔墨斯号\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} They can take over the Hermes from Mission Control.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.78,1:29:44.88,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你能让他们控制不了么?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Can you disable it?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.91,1:29:47.15,Chinese,,0,0,0,,赫尔墨斯号有4个多余的飞行用电脑\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Hermes has 4 redundant flight computers,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.16,1:29:49.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,每一个都连接着3个通讯系统\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} each connected to 3 redundant comm systems.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.72,1:29:52.60,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们不能把通信切断, 因为我们还需要遥感和指引\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} We can't shut down the comms, because we'll lose telemetry and guidance.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:52.63,1:29:56.10,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们也不能把飞行用电脑关掉, 要不就不能操控飞船了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} And we can't shut down the computers, because we need to run the ship.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.12,1:29:59.49,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我必须得人为禁止每个电脑上的远程操控系统\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} I'll have to disable remote override on each system.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.52,1:30:01.65,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这是它系统的一部分, 我得跳过这些代码\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} It's part of the OS, I have to jump over the code.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.67,1:30:04.89,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好, 所以用人话来说是什么意思?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Okay, but like in English, like what would that mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.57,1:30:08.31,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我能关掉远程遥控系统\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.79,1:30:10.25,Chinese,,0,0,0,,牛逼\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Great.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.40,1:30:13.64,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但我们必须意见一致\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} But, it has to be unanimous.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.66,1:30:18.88,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们如果决定了, 那就要在宇宙中呆900多天\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} If we do this, it will be over 900 days of space.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.66,1:30:24.64,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这比任何人一辈子应该在宇宙中带的时间还要多, 所以\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} It's more than enough space for 1 life, so...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.17,1:30:26.51,Chinese,,0,0,0,,就这么做!\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.54,1:30:28.25,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我同意\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} I vote yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.29,1:30:32.13,Chinese,,0,0,0,,走, 咱去接他\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Let's go get him.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.91,1:30:36.68,Chinese,,0,0,0,,约翰森?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Johanssen?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.85,1:30:38.04,Chinese,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.08,1:30:39.97,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 耶 - 耶!\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} - Yeah. - Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.51,1:30:44.07,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们收到了一个赫尔墨斯号非计划中的状态提醒\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Got an unscheduled status update from Hermes.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.09,1:30:45.46,Chinese,,0,0,0,,收到, 读出来\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Roger, read it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.46,1:30:47.62,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这条信息说: “休斯顿, 请注意:\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Message reads: 'Houston, please be advised:
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.65,1:30:49.98,Chinese,,0,0,0,,里奇·珀内尔是一个目光坚定的火箭人\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Rich Purnell is a steely- eyed missile man.'
Dialogue: 0,1:30:50.01,1:30:51.17,Chinese,,0,0,0,,什么鬼?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} What?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.20,1:30:52.85,Chinese,,0,0,0,,飞行, 指示\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Flight, Guidance.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.88,1:30:54.48,Chinese,,0,0,0,,赫尔墨斯号脱离了航线\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Hermes is off course.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.49,1:30:57.79,Chinese,,0,0,0,,总部, 注意赫尔墨斯号脱离了航线 引导员, 准备一个校对方案\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} CAPCOM, advise Hermes they're drifting. Guidance, get a correction ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.81,1:31:00.97,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不对, 总部 不是一个航线漂移, 他们自己改变的航线\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Negative, Flight. It's not adrift. They adjusted course.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.99,1:31:02.13,Chinese,,0,0,0,,什么鬼?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.16,1:31:05.08,Chinese,,0,0,0,,遥测部门, 有没有可能是设备故障?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Telemetry, any chance this is instrumentation failure?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.11,1:31:06.27,Chinese,,0,0,0,,没有, 控制总部\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}  Negative, Flight.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.30,1:31:10.07,Chinese,,0,0,0,,引导员, 会计算一下他们偏离多久就改不回原来的航线了?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Guidance, work out how long they can stay on this course before it's irreversible?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:10.09,1:31:12.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,正在计算, 总部\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Working on that now, Flight.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.21,1:31:13.89,Chinese,,0,0,0,,谁是里奇·珀内尔?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Who's Rich Purnell?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.91,1:31:15.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我不清楚\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.30,1:31:18.39,Chinese,,0,0,0,,快点有谁能他妈告诉我谁是里奇·珀内尔!\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} And somebody find out who the hell  Rich Purnell is!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.47,1:31:20.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,安妮会在新闻发布会之前\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Annie will go before the media this morning
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.39,1:31:25.21,Chinese,,0,0,0,,告诉他们美航局决定让赫尔墨斯号更改航道回到火星\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} and inform them of NASA's decision to reroute the Hermes to Mars.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.23,1:31:27.39,Chinese,,0,0,0,,明智之举\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Sounds like a smart move.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.90,1:31:30.48,Chinese,,0,0,0,,想想看后果\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Considering the circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.73,1:31:35.46,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不管是谁给他们的这个任务调遣, 只是传递了以下信息而已\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Whoever gave them the maneuver, only passed along information.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.48,1:31:37.94,Chinese,,0,0,0,,宇航员们自己做出了他们的决定\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} The crew made the decision on their own.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.11,1:31:41.54,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你可能就这样断送了他们的性命啊, Mitch\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} You may have killed them, Mitch.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:43.08,1:31:44.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们利益共存\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} We're fighting the same war.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:44.98,1:31:48.27,Chinese,,0,0,0,,每次出事故, 大家都会忘记我们为什么要去太空旅行\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Every time something goes wrong, the world forgets why we fly.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.29,1:31:50.14,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我只是想让咱们继续在空中飞着\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} I'm trying to keep us airborne.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.16,1:31:52.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,远远比一个人的性命重要得多\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} It's bigger than 1 person.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.97,1:31:55.57,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} No.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.59,1:31:57.22,Chinese,,0,0,0,,并不是这样\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} It's not.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.93,1:32:02.07,Chinese,,0,0,0,,等这件事情过去, 我等着你的辞职信\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} When this is over, I'll expect your resignation.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.98,1:32:06.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我明白了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} I understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.44,1:32:09.07,Chinese,,0,0,0,,把我们的宇航员带回家吧\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Bring our astronauts home.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.76,1:32:11.99,Chinese,,0,0,0,,第219太阳日\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} SOL 219
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.02,1:32:14.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好的每个阿瑞斯任务都有三年期的任务前供给\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Okay. Every Ares mission requires 3 years of pre- supplies.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.91,1:32:17.65,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以美国航天局很久之前就决定了早一些送补给到火星\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} So NASA decided a long time ago it's a lot easier to
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.65,1:32:20.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,比带着补给飞过来要容易得多\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} send some of this stuff beforehand rather than bring it with us.
