Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.40,1:32:31.35,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以现在的计划就是我用它飞到火星轨道\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} So, the plan is for me to use that to go into orbit
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.37,1:32:34.46,Chinese,,0,0,0,,正好当赫尔墨斯好经过,\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}  just as the Hermes is passing,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.49,1:32:38.32,Chinese,,0,0,0,,然后在宇宙中\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} And I guess they catch me
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.84,1:32:40.92,Chinese,,0,0,0,,接住我\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} in space.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:42.88,1:32:45.97,Chinese,,0,0,0,,然后, 我就得想想看怎么再度过200太阳日\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} So, I've got 200 Sols to figure out
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.98,1:32:48.81,Chinese,,0,0,0,,然后带着所有能让我活命的东西过去：\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} how to take everything here that keeping me alive:
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.81,1:32:52.65,Chinese,,0,0,0,,氧气供给, 水循环系统, 大气调节器\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} The oxygenator, the water reclaimer, the atmospheric regulator.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.68,1:32:54.60,Chinese,,0,0,0,,带着这么一大堆东西\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Bring that all with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.63,1:32:58.46,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是幸运的是我有全球最聪明的一帮人帮我\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} And luckily I have the- the greatest minds on planet Earth,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.46,1:33:01.71,Chinese,,0,0,0,,真的, 全球的聪明才智,\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} really, all of the brain power of the entire planet,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.74,1:33:03.66,Chinese,,0,0,0,,在帮我走出这个困境\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} helping me with this endeavor.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.66,1:33:05.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,现在呢, 我们有了以下想法,\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} And so far they've come up with,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.39,1:33:07.97,Chinese,,0,0,0,,“嘿, 为啥不在你的探险车顶上钻孔呢\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} "Hey, why don't you drill holes in the roof of your Rover
Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.00,1:33:10.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,然后用石头使劲敲他“\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} and hit it as hard as you can with a rock."
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.29,1:33:13.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我觉得我们能达到目的地\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} We're going to get there.
