Dialogue: 0,1:34:12.79,1:34:15.21,Chinese,,0,0,0,,再待533天?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} 533 days longer?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.21,1:34:17.29,Chinese,,0,0,0,,然后你同意了?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} And you said yes to this?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.31,1:34:20.05,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你知道要是我被困住了, 他也会为了我这么做的\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} He would have done the same for me. You know that.
