Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.45,1:34:52.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,跟新的一样\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Not a scratch.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:52.73,1:34:54.10,Chinese,,0,0,0,,喜欢的不得了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} I love it.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:54.11,1:34:56.94,Chinese,,0,0,0,,根据CNSA协议\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} With all due respect to your CNSA protocols ,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:56.97,1:34:59.31,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但- 但我们很久没有那么干了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} but- but we haven't done things that way
