Dialogue: 0,1:37:40.13,1:37:43.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,第461太阳日\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} SOL 461
Dialogue: 0,1:38:14.55,1:38:17.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我一直在思考关于火星的法律部法规\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} I've thinking about laws on Mars.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:17.39,1:38:19.91,Chinese,,0,0,0,,有国际法说没有任何国家\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} There's an international treaty saying no country can lay claim
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.93,1:38:21.62,Chinese,,0,0,0,,可以说地球以外的任何东西属于他们\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} to anything that is not on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.65,1:38:25.01,Chinese,,0,0,0,,另外一个跳跃又说了, 若你不在任何国土上,\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} And by another treaty,, if you're not in any countries territory,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.03,1:38:26.83,Chinese,,0,0,0,,就得遵循海上的法律\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}  Maritime law applies.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:26.86,1:38:30.41,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以火星应该算是”国际海域“\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} So, Mars is "international waters."
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.52,1:38:33.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,现在, NASA是美国非军事化的组织,\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Now, NASA is an American nonmilitary organization,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:33.70,1:38:35.13,Chinese,,0,0,0,,科研站属于它\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} it owns the hab.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:35.16,1:38:38.03,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是当我走出科研站, 我就在国际海域中了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} But, the second I walk outside, I'm in international waters.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:38.03,1:38:39.53,Chinese,,0,0,0,,然后啊, 就有意思了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} So, here's the cool part.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:39.53,1:38:41.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我现在正在前往斯基阿帕雷利陨石坑\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} I'm about to leave for the Schiaparelli crater
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.24,1:38:43.29,Chinese,,0,0,0,,然后要征用阿瑞斯4的着陆器\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} where I'm going to commandeer the Ares 4 Lander.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:43.32,1:38:45.64,Chinese,,0,0,0,,没有人给我直接的指示去这么干,\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Nobody explicitly gave me permission to this,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:45.66,1:38:48.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,直到我登上阿瑞斯4 之前都不能给我任何指示\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} and they can't until I'm on board the Ares 4.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.30,1:38:50.01,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这样, 我就成了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} So, that means I'm going to be
Dialogue: 0,1:38:50.04,1:38:53.59,Chinese,,0,0,0,,在国际海域未经许可的接管了一艘舰艇\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} taking over a craft over in international waters without permission.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:53.62,1:38:57.96,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这样, 根据定义, 就让我成为了一个海盗\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Which, by definition, makes me a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:58.55,1:39:02.61,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 马克·沃特尼, 宇宙海盗第461天\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- Mark Watney, space pirate. [SOL 461]
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.12,1:39:07.04,Chinese,,0,0,0,,系统关闭\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} systems shutdown
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.06,1:39:08.85,Chinese,,0,0,0,,关闭完成\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} shutdown complete
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.79,1:39:33.88,Chinese,,0,0,0,,宇宙海盗\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Space pirate.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:34.15,1:40:38.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我管我去哪我都是第一个\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Wherever I go, I'm the first.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.70,1:40:40.91,Chinese,,0,0,0,,真是一个奇妙的感觉\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} It's a strange feeling.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.99,1:40:42.55,Chinese,,0,0,0,,从探险车走出来,\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Step outside the Rover,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:42.57,1:40:44.65,Chinese,,0,0,0,,第一人\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} first guy to be there.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.02,1:40:48.46,Chinese,,0,0,0,,爬那座上, 第一个那么做的人\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Climb that hill, first guy to do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.29,1:40:51.64,Chinese,,0,0,0,,45亿年,\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} 4.5 billion years,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.67,1:40:53.52,Chinese,,0,0,0,,从没人来过\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} nobody here.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.54,1:40:56.87,Chinese,,0,0,0,,今天, 我在这\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} And now, me.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:57.63,1:41:01.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我是第一个单独在一个星球上待着的男人\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} I'm the first person to be alone on an entire planet.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.31,1:41:17.93,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他怎么样?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} How's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:19.36,1:41:21.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,还不错\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} So far so good.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.24,1:41:23.42,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他在按着计划前行\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} He's... sticking to schedule.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:23.45,1:41:26.34,Chinese,,0,0,0,,在中午前4小时一直前进,\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Directs for 4 hours before noon,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.65,1:41:29.75,Chinese,,0,0,0,,放好太阳能板, 等13小时让他们充好电,\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Lays the solar panels, waits 13 hours for them to recharge,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:29.77,1:41:34.81,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这期间找个地方睡一觉, 然后重新开始\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} and sleeps somewhere in there and then, starts again.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.51,1:41:38.15,Chinese,,0,0,0,,有何进展啊?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} How's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:39.66,1:41:42.81,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它让我们叫它, 大胡子船长\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} He asked us to call him, Captain Longbeard.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.49,1:41:46.62,Chinese,,0,0,0,,因为, 按理来说, 火星是隶属航洋法的\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Well, technically, Mars would be under maritime laws.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.64,1:41:48.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我懂, 我懂他都跟我们解释过了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} I know, I know. He explained it to us.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.17,1:41:51.94,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他在哪?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:52.44,1:41:54.07,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 这- 好\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} - Here. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:54.09,1:41:55.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Here.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.66,1:41:57.26,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.26,1:42:05.64,Chinese,,0,0,0,,第494太阳日\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} SOL 494
Dialogue: 0,1:43:36.23,1:43:40.27,Chinese,,0,0,0,,第517太阳日\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} SOL 517
Dialogue: 0,1:43:40.89,1:43:42.92,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们要开门见山地说了,\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Okay, we're going to start by stating,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:42.95,1:43:44.94,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你估计是不会喜欢我要告诉你的\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} for the record, that you're not going to like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:44.96,1:43:46.58,Chinese,,0,0,0,,哦, 真的么?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:46.84,1:43:49.31,Chinese,,0,0,0,,是啊相遇速度有点问题\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Yeah. The problem is the intercept velocity.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:49.34,1:43:54.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,赫尔墨斯号不能进入火星的轨道\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} The Hermes. Well, they, it can't enter Mars orbit.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:54.21,1:43:57.65,Chinese,,0,0,0,,要不他们就没有足够的燃料回家了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Otherwise, they will never have enough fuel to, make it home.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:57.68,1:44:02.47,Chinese,,0,0,0,,飞行器只是为了到火星低位轨道设计的\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} The MAV was only designed to get to low Mars orbit.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:02.50,1:44:06.63,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以想让马克完全脱离火星的引力,\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} So, in order for Mark to escape Mars gravity entirely,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:06.66,1:44:08.08,Chinese,,0,0,0,,然后和赫尔墨斯号相遇\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} and to intercept the Hermes...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:08.10,1:44:09.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 他必须够快- 没错\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} - He has to be going fast. - Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:09.92,1:44:12.34,Chinese,,0,0,0,,就意味着我得让飞行器足够轻\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Which means we need to make the MAV lighter.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:12.37,1:44:15.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,比之前要轻5000公斤\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} A lot lighter. 5000 kg lighter.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:15.03,1:44:16.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但, 这是能做到的, 对吧?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} But, you can do that, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.40,1:44:18.33,Chinese,,0,0,0,,能是能, 但是得耍些小手段\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Well, there's some gimmes right off the bat.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:18.35,1:44:21.87,Chinese,,0,0,0,,设计是要带回500公斤的火星土壤和标本\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} The design presumes 500 kg of Martian soil and samples.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:21.87,1:44:23.59,Chinese,,0,0,0,,很明显我们不会那么做\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Obviously we won't do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:23.61,1:44:27.32,Chinese,,0,0,0,,相对于6个宇航员, 我们现在只需要考虑一个人\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} And there's just 1 passenger instead of 6.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:27.34,1:44:30.03,Chinese,,0,0,0,,算上宇航服和装备, 又是500公斤?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} With suits and gear, that's another 500?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:30.06,1:44:32.12,Chinese,,0,0,0,,扔了维持生命的设备 不需要这些\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Ditch the support of life. We don't need it.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:32.12,1:44:34.56,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们要让马克在整个过程中穿自己的宇航服\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} And I'm going to make Mark to wear his EVA suit for the whole trip.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:34.58,1:44:37.29,Chinese,,0,0,0,,等等!如果他穿着宇航服, 谁控制飞行器呢?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Wait a second! If he's in his EVA suit, How's he going to operate the controls?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:37.32,1:44:39.63,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这么看来, 他就不能控制了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Well, he won't.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:39.63,1:44:43.43,Chinese,,0,0,0,,马丁内斯负责从赫尔墨斯号操控飞行器\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Martinez will pilot the MAV remotely from the Hermes.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:43.43,1:44:47.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们从来没有尝试过远程操控有人搭载的航天器\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} We've never had a manned ship controlled remotely before.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.68,1:44:52.23,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是我对于有这样的机会感到很兴奋啊\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} But I am excited about the opportunities that I forged.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:52.25,1:44:56.99,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如果我们搞远程操控, 控制台, 通讯设备也都不需要了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} If we go remote, we can lose the control panels, the secondary, tertiary comm systems.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:57.01,1:44:58.80,Chinese,,0,0,0,,等... 等一下......你要干嘛?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Wait. Wait a second. You want to what?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:58.83,1:45:02.87,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你想远程操控一个没有备用通讯设施的升空中的航天器?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} You want to remotely controlled ascent with no backup comms?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:03.78,1:45:06.22,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他还没说到最坏的部分呢, 文森特\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} He's not even got to the bad stuff yet, Vincent.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:06.24,1:45:08.34,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好吧, 说说最坏的把!\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Well, let's get to the bad stuff!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:08.36,1:45:13.86,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们需要移除顶部密封层, 窗户, 和面板19.\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} We need to remove the nose airlock, the windows and Hull Panel 19.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:14.40,1:45:16.22,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你想把整个飞行器的前面都拆了?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} You want to take the front of the ship off?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:16.25,1:45:17.38,Chinese,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:17.38,1:45:20.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,顶部的气密舱有400公斤重呢\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} The nose airlock alone is 400 kg.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:20.52,1:45:22.86,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你想用一个连头都没有的飞行器送一个人到太空?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} You want to send a man into space without the front of his ship?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:22.89,1:45:24.35,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不，不是的\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Well, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:25.13,1:45:29.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们将用飞船的帆布罩住他\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} We're going to have him cover it with Hab canvas.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:29.96,1:45:32.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,外壳是为了保持舱内的空气\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} The hull's mostly there to keep the air.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:32.93,1:45:36.07,Chinese,,0,0,0,,火星的大气很薄，不需要让机舱太流线化\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Mars atmosphere is so thin, you don't need a lot of streamlining.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:36.08,1:45:39.58,Chinese,,0,0,0,,等到飞船的速度快到会受空气阻力影响的时候，\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} By the time the ship's going fast enough for air resistance to matter,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:39.58,1:45:42.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,就应该已经到达没有多少空气的高度了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}  it'll be high enough that there's practically no air.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:42.21,1:45:45.08,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你想让他在一块布的包裹下到太空中去\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} You want to send him into space under a tarp.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:45.10,1:45:46.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:47.22,1:45:48.89,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我能继续了么?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Can I go on?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:48.91,1:45:50.30,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不行\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} No.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:51.42,1:45:54.15,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你他妈的在逗我?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Are you f---ing kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:56.45,1:45:58.65,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我觉得他是想说，\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} You think he means it like,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:59.10,1:46:01.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你在逗我?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:01.12,1:46:02.41,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 懂我的意思么? - 哼 - 哼\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} - You know? - Um- hum.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:02.44,1:46:05.87,Chinese,,0,0,0,,或者是,"你在逗我?"\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Or like, "Are you kidding me?"
Dialogue: 0,1:46:06.34,1:46:08.32,Chinese,,0,0,0,,有可能是二个\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} I think it might be the second one.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:08.34,1:46:09.91,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 真的么? - 哼\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} - Really? - Uh- huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:09.94,1:46:12.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,也有可能是第一个\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Could be the first one.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:12.15,1:46:14.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你在逗我?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:14.26,1:46:16.47,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这么一想，也有可能是第一个\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Yeah, it could be the first one.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:23.98,1:46:27.23,Chinese,,0,0,0,,第538太阳日\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} SOL 538
Dialogue: 0,1:46:28.97,1:46:33.86,Chinese,,0,0,0,,基阿帕雷利陨石坑，阿瑞斯4着陆地点\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} SCHIAPARELLI CRATER Ares 4 LANDING SITE
Dialogue: 0,1:46:40.15,1:46:42.41,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我知道他们要干嘛\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}  I know what they are doing.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:43.49,1:46:46.05,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我能猜到他们的每一步计划\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} I know exactly what they are doing.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:46.15,1:46:48.02,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他们一直在重复，\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} 'Cause they're keep repeating,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:48.02,1:46:51.31,Chinese,,0,0,0,,想要作为宇宙旅行的先驱者\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Go faster than any man in the history of space travel.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:51.34,1:46:52.62,Chinese,,0,0,0,,就像是个好的成就一样\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Like that's a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:52.64,1:46:55.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好像就能让我忽视掉他们计划的疯狂程度\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Like it would distract me from how insane their plan is.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:56.29,1:46:59.99,Chinese,,0,0,0,,没错 我确实得飞得比任何人类都快\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Yeah. I get to go faster than any man in the history of space travel.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:59.99,1:47:03.04,Chinese,,0,0,0,,应为你让我在一架敞篷里面发射\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Because you're launching me in a convertible.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:03.04,1:47:06.87,Chinese,,0,0,0,,说实话，更烂，因为我根本没法控制\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Actually, it's worse than that, because I won't be able to control that thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:06.88,1:47:12.38,Chinese,,0,0,0,,顺被提一句，物理学家，他们形容速度的时候，\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} And by the way, physicists, when describing things like acceleration,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:12.40,1:47:15.60,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不用快不快 所以\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}  do not use the word 'fast'. So...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:15.62,1:47:20.52,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他们这么做，希望我不产生任何异议\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} They're doing that, in the hopes that I won't raise any objections.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:20.84,1:47:23.14,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这么做简直是疯了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} It's a lunacy.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:23.82,1:47:25.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你以为，因我喜欢，\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} You think, because I like the way,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:25.31,1:47:28.47,Chinese,,0,0,0,,‘宇宙探索史上飞得最快的男人’的说法\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} 'The fastest man in the history of space travel.' sounds.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:30.06,1:47:32.42,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我还真挺喜欢这称号\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} I do like the way it sounds.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:33.36,1:47:35.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,太尼玛喜欢了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Yeah, I like it a lot.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:37.57,1:47:39.81,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我不会这么告诉他的\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} I'm not going to tell them that.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:45.74,1:47:47.22,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好的吧\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:48.46,1:47:50.15,Chinese,,0,0,0,,开始干\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:25.48,1:48:27.14,Chinese,,0,0,0,,加油\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:57.24,1:48:59.11,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\c&H8080FF&}[权限拒绝]{\c}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:03.11,1:49:05.17,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\c&H8080FF&}[权限拒绝]{\c}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:21.40,1:50:23.79,Chinese,,0,0,0,,贝克和沃格尔去2号气密舱\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Beck and Vogel. I want you guys in airlock 2.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:23.80,1:50:26.15,Chinese,,0,0,0,,在MAV发射之前把外侧的门打开\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} With the outer door open before the MAV even launches.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:26.17,1:50:26.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,收到\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:26.84,1:50:30.68,Chinese,,0,0,0,,马丁内斯来操控MAV，约翰森负责总控制\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Martinez flies the MAV, Johanssen sysop the ascent.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:30.70,1:50:34.67,Chinese,,0,0,0,,当我们相遇时，贝克负责去接沃特尼\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Once we hit intercept, it's Beck's job to go get Watney.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:34.67,1:50:35.79,Chinese,,0,0,0,,准备就绪\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} We're ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:35.82,1:50:37.83,Chinese,,0,0,0,,拦截计划具体是什么样的?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} What's the intercept plan?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:37.85,1:50:40.31,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们把绳子系成一长条\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} We finished attaching the tethers into 1 long line
Dialogue: 0,1:50:40.34,1:50:42.51,Chinese,,0,0,0,,214米长一共\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} It's 214 meters long.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:42.52,1:50:45.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我将会驾驶这MMU，所以在宇宙中移动不成问题\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} And I'll have the MMU, so moving around should be easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:45.27,1:50:48.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你能应付的对快相对速度是多少?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} How fast a relative velocity can you handle?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:48.22,1:50:50.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,5米每秒我就能抓住MAV\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} I can grab the MAV at 5 meters per second.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:50.95,1:50:52.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,10米每秒就像网一辆火车上跳\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Ten is like jumping onto a moving train.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:52.87,1:50:55.32,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以如果比这个速度快，我不一定抓得住\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} So, any more than that, I might miss.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:55.35,1:50:57.79,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这样啊，我们有可能有些余地\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Well, we may have some leeway.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:58.73,1:51:00.73,Chinese,,0,0,0,,发射过程共12分钟\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} The launch takes 12 minutes,
Dialogue: 0,1:51:00.76,1:51:03.74,Chinese,,0,0,0,,会在拦截前52分钟发射\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} and it will be 52 minutes before intercept.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:03.76,1:51:05.47,Chinese,,0,0,0,,一旦马克的引擎关掉，\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Once Mark's engines shut off,
Dialogue: 0,1:51:05.50,1:51:09.13,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们就能知道拦截地点和相对速度了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} we'll know our intercept point and velocity.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:09.16,1:51:10.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,沃格尔，你是贝克的替补\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Vogel, you're Beck's backup.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:10.86,1:51:13.64,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如果进行的顺利，你把他们俩一起拽回来\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Everything goes well, you pull them on board with the tether.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:13.67,1:51:16.47,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如果有失误，去救他回来\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} If anything goes wrong, you go out after him.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:16.50,1:51:17.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,没问题\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:17.86,1:51:19.39,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:21.09,1:51:23.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,咱们去把他接回来\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Let's go get our boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:25.58,1:51:30.96,Chinese,,0,0,0,,第562太阳日\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} SOL 561
Dialogue: 0,1:51:57.39,1:52:02.69,Chinese,,0,0,0,,至不论是谁，好好对这台探险车，他救了我的命 沃特尼\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} To whom it may concern, take care of this Rover. She saved my life. Watney.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:24.76,1:52:28.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,在约翰逊航天中心外有很多紧张焦虑的人们\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} There's a mood of tension and anxiety here, outside Johnson Space Center.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:28.26,1:52:30.80,Chinese,,0,0,0,,就像你能看到的一样，很多人来看，\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} As you can see, many people have gathered here,
Dialogue: 0,1:52:30.83,1:52:36.10,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这次的拯救行动是否能够成功, 就看我们是否救到了沃特尼\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} To see whether or not, the mission to retrieve Mark Watney will be a success.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:36.13,1:52:38.05,Chinese,,0,0,0,,要记得，他们用了某些方式联系到他\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Remember, they had some kind of contact with him.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:38.08,1:52:39.29,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是我们并不能得到很多信息\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} but it hasn't been very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:39.32,1:52:43.27,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以我们必须时刻提醒我们的观众随着时间的继续发展\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} We have to remind our viewers that we're watching this as it unfolds
Dialogue: 0,1:52:43.30,1:52:47.05,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们也会跟观众随时更新动态\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} and we'll try to keep you up to date as to what exactly is going on.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:47.07,1:52:50.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们现在听听美航局跟马克·沃特尼的连线\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Let's listen in to NASA, making contact with Mark Watney.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:50.93,1:52:52.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,大家一起听\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Let's listen in.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:58.86,1:53:01.66,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如果有任何差错，总控制中心能干什么么?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} If something goes wrong, What can Mission Control do?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:01.69,1:53:03.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,啥都做不了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Not a damn thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:04.36,1:53:06.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,12分钟之后就要开始了，\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} It's all happening 12 light minutes away,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:06.28,1:53:10.82,Chinese,,0,0,0,,就意味着要花他们24分钟得到任何他们想问的问题的答案\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} which means it takes 24 minutes for them to get the answer to any question they ask.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:11.11,1:53:13.75,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们将在12分钟后发射，所以\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Our launch is just 12 minutes, so...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:14.96,1:53:16.79,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他们的靠自己了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} They're on their own.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:07.04,1:54:08.05,Chinese,,0,0,0,,中国航天局 北京总部\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} CNSA HEADQUARTERS BEIJING
Dialogue: 0,1:54:08.08,1:54:11.73,Chinese,,0,0,0,,今天，不管是北京人，全世界的人群聚集在电视前，\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Today, people have gathered in front of the TVs in Beijing and all over the world,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:11.76,1:54:15.01,Chinese,,0,0,0,,关注着这个牵动全世界的救援行动\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} watching attentively at the rescue mission which have caught the attention of the whole world.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:15.03,1:54:20.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这次任务的可行性，是因为中国 NSA的无私\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} This rescue made possible, is due to China NSA's selfless....
Dialogue: 0,1:54:20.31,1:54:21.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,特拉法加广场，伦敦\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} TRAFALGAR SQUARE LONDON
Dialogue: 0,1:54:21.75,1:54:23.63,Chinese,,0,0,0,,马克完全一个人孤单的在火星上\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Mark has been completely alone on Mars.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:23.65,1:54:27.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,根据心理学家的说法\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} According to psychology expert, they said...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:49.76,1:54:51.65,Chinese,,0,0,0,,燃油压力正常\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Fuel pressure green.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:51.67,1:54:54.01,Chinese,,0,0,0,,引擎校准完美\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Engine alignment perfect.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:54.01,1:54:56.74,Chinese,,0,0,0,,通没有问题\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Communications 5 by 5.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:56.83,1:55:00.38,Chinese,,0,0,0,,指挥官，我们可以进行与发射检查了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} We are ready for preflight checklist, Commander.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:00.41,1:55:04.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,总智慧，这里是赫尔墨斯号 我们将按原计划执行\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Mission Control, this is Hermes Actual. We will proceed on schedule.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:04.75,1:55:09.13,Chinese,,0,0,0,,还有2分10秒发射\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} We are 2 min 10 sec to launch, by the mark.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:09.57,1:55:11.98,Chinese,,0,0,0,,大概两分钟，沃特尼你怎么样?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} About 2 minutes, Watney. How are you doing down there?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:11.98,1:55:13.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,棒极了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:14.03,1:55:16.21,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我等不及上去见你\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} I'm anxious to get up to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:16.37,1:55:17.87,Chinese,,0,0,0,,感谢你们回来救我\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Thanks for coming back for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:17.87,1:55:18.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不客气 马上要开始了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Yeah. We're on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:18.95,1:55:20.71,Chinese,,0,0,0,,记得，你会承受很多倍的加速度\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Remember, you'll be pulling some serious g's.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:20.74,1:55:22.59,Chinese,,0,0,0,,晕过去没问题的\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} So, it's okay to pass out.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:22.59,1:55:24.51,Chinese,,0,0,0,,马丁内斯将会控制你的飞船\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} You're in Martinez's hands now.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:24.53,1:55:28.05,Chinese,,0,0,0,,告诉他，不要让飞船瞎翻来翻去的\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Well. Tell that asshole no barrel rolls.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:28.72,1:55:30.58,Chinese,,0,0,0,,收到，飞行器\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Copy that, MAV.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:30.60,1:55:31.81,Chinese,,0,0,0,,通讯\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} CAPCOM.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:31.83,1:55:32.78,Chinese,,0,0,0,,就绪\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Go.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:32.80,1:55:33.99,Chinese,,0,0,0,,远程控制指令\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Remote Command.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:33.99,1:55:34.99,Chinese,,0,0,0,,就绪\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Go.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:34.99,1:55:35.99,Chinese,,0,0,0,,救回\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Recovery.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:35.99,1:55:36.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,就绪\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Go.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:36.99,1:55:38.61,Chinese,,0,0,0,,副救回\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Secondary recovery.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:38.61,1:55:39.78,Chinese,,0,0,0,,就绪\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Go.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:39.78,1:55:41.31,Chinese,,0,0,0,,飞行员\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Pilot.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:42.13,1:55:43.08,Chinese,,0,0,0,,就绪\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Go.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:43.11,1:55:44.48,Chinese,,0,0,0,,飞行员\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Pilot.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:44.48,1:55:45.77,Chinese,,0,0,0,,就绪\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Go.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:45.77,1:55:47.42,Chinese,,0,0,0,,收到 我们准备出发\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Copy. We're a go.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:47.94,1:55:51.12,Chinese,,0,0,0,,指挥部，我们准备发射了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Mission Control. We are go for launch.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:51.15,1:55:52.48,Chinese,,0,0,0,,倒计时 10，\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} T minus 10,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:52.51,1:55:54.67,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 9.- 主引擎打火\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} - 9. - Main engine start.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:54.70,1:55:56.30,Chinese,,0,0,0,,8.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:56.33,1:55:57.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,7.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:57.42,1:55:59.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,系泊夹放开\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Mooring clamps released.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:59.16,1:56:00.91,Chinese,,0,0,0,,还5秒，沃特尼 准备好\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} About 5 seconds, Watney. Hang on.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:00.93,1:56:02.85,Chinese,,0,0,0,,待会见，指挥官\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} See you in a few, Commander.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:02.88,1:56:04.51,Chinese,,0,0,0,,4.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:04.66,1:56:06.07,Chinese,,0,0,0,,3.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:06.26,1:56:07.73,Chinese,,0,0,0,,2.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:07.93,1:56:09.34,Chinese,,0,0,0,,1.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:45.04,1:56:47.57,Chinese,,0,0,0,,速度，741米每秒\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Velocity, 741 meters per second.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:47.60,1:56:49.62,Chinese,,0,0,0,,高度，1350米\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Altitude, 1350 meters.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:49.65,1:56:50.75,Chinese,,0,0,0,,飞的不够高\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} It's too low.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:50.77,1:56:52.56,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我知道，他不让我飞得更高\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} I know. It's fighting me.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:56.09,1:56:59.96,Chinese,,0,0,0,,沃特尼，听得到么?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Watney, do you read?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:05.09,1:57:06.77,Chinese,,0,0,0,,助推器分离完毕\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Booster separation complete.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:06.77,1:57:09.74,Chinese,,0,0,0,,速度，850. 高度，1843.\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Velocity, 850. Altitude, 1843.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:09.76,1:57:11.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他离目标的高度差太远了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} He's way below target altitude.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:11.30,1:57:13.15,Chinese,,0,0,0,,差多少?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} How- How far below?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:13.17,1:57:14.71,Chinese,,0,0,0,,正在查\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Checking.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:14.90,1:57:18.12,Chinese,,0,0,0,,沃特尼，收到么?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Watney, do you read?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:18.15,1:57:19.35,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他估计晕过去了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} He's probably passed out
Dialogue: 0,1:57:19.38,1:57:21.96,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他承受了12个G的加速度 让他缓一缓\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} He pulled 12 g's on the ascent. Give him a few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:21.98,1:57:23.46,Chinese,,0,0,0,,收到\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Copy that.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:25.47,1:57:27.47,Chinese,,0,0,0,,3秒主助推器熄火，\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Main shutdown in 3,
Dialogue: 0,1:57:27.49,1:57:28.51,Chinese,,0,0,0,,2\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} 2,
Dialogue: 0,1:57:28.54,1:57:29.78,Chinese,,0,0,0,,1\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} 1.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:29.80,1:57:31.35,Chinese,,0,0,0,,熄火\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Shutdown.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:32.38,1:57:34.49,Chinese,,0,0,0,,回到自动导航\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Back to automatic guidance.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:34.52,1:57:36.57,Chinese,,0,0,0,,已确认熄火\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Shutdown confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:38.70,1:57:40.92,Chinese,,0,0,0,,燃料储备用尽\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Fuel reserve depleted.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:42.40,1:57:43.79,Chinese,,0,0,0,,沃特尼,\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Watney
Dialogue: 0,1:57:44.10,1:57:45.93,Chinese,,0,0,0,,收到么?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} do you read?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:46.41,1:57:49.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,看来可能有一些通讯上的问题\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} There seems to be some sort of problem with the transmission.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:56.17,1:57:57.86,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我有时间延迟\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} I have interval pings.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:57.86,1:58:00.07,Chinese,,0,0,0,,拦截速度将会是11米每秒\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Intercept velocity will be 11 meters per second.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:00.07,1:58:02.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我能接下来\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} I can make that work.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:02.46,1:58:05.22,Chinese,,0,0,0,,距离差将会是\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Distance at intercept will be...
Dialogue: 0,1:58:05.25,1:58:07.35,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们将会相距68公里\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} We'll be 68 km apart.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:07.37,1:58:09.43,Chinese,,0,0,0,,68 千米\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} 68 km?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:09.46,1:58:12.07,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他刚刚说68公里?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Did she just say 68 km?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:12.59,1:58:15.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,别瞎闹，解决眼前的问题\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Come on, guys, keep it together. Work the problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:15.38,1:58:17.71,Chinese,,0,0,0,,约翰森，拦截时间?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Johanssen, time to intercept?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:17.74,1:58:20.39,Chinese,,0,0,0,,还有39分钟12秒\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} 39 minutes 12 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:20.41,1:58:23.49,Chinese,,0,0,0,,马丁内斯，不如把我们的助推器指向他的方向?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Martinez, what if we point our thrusters in the same direction?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:23.52,1:58:26.01,Chinese,,0,0,0,,就看你想保留多少燃料了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Well, it depends on how much fuel you want to save
Dialogue: 0,1:58:26.03,1:58:28.14,Chinese,,0,0,0,,回地球的时候还要调整高度\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} for the altitude adjustments for the trip home.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:28.14,1:58:29.41,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你需要多少?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} How much do you need?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:29.43,1:58:34.07,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我应该能用20%剩下的燃料办到\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} I can get by with about 20% of what we have left.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:34.31,1:58:38.12,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如果我们用75.5%剩下的燃料调整高度，\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} If we use 75.5% of remaining altitude adjustment fuel,
Dialogue: 0,1:58:38.15,1:58:40.56,Chinese,,0,0,0,,就能让距离差为0.\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} That'll bring the intercept range to zero.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:40.58,1:58:42.14,Chinese,,0,0,0,,干吧\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:42.16,1:58:44.61,Chinese,,0,0,0,,等一下 虽说距离为零了，\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Hang on. It brings the range to zero,
Dialogue: 0,1:58:44.64,1:58:48.22,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是拦截相对速度将会变成42米每秒\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} but the intercept velocity will be 42 meters per second.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:48.24,1:58:50.23,Chinese,,0,0,0,,太他妈快了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} And it's way too fast.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:50.42,1:58:54.29,Chinese,,0,0,0,,现在就需要在39分钟里思考出来怎么慢下来\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Then, we have 39 minutes to figure out how to slow down.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:57.01,1:58:58.94,Chinese,,0,0,0,,马丁内斯，点火\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Martinez, burn the jets.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:58.97,1:59:00.52,Chinese,,0,0,0,,收到\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Copy that.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:22.74,1:59:24.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,飞行器呼叫 赫尔墨斯号\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Mav to Hermes.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:24.95,1:59:26.03,Chinese,,0,0,0,,沃特尼?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:26.05,1:59:27.82,Chinese,,0,0,0,,确认\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Affirmative.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:31.07,1:59:32.83,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你状况如何?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} What's your status?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:32.85,1:59:34.85,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我胸口好疼\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} My chest hurts.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:34.88,1:59:37.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,可能肋骨断了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} I have broken my ribs.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:37.12,1:59:38.31,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你怎么样?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} How are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:38.34,1:59:41.17,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们正在考虑怎么救你 过程中出了个小问题\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} We're working on getting to you. There was a complication during the launch.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:41.17,1:59:42.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,收到\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Copy that.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:43.10,1:59:44.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这样啊，什么样的小问题?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Well, how bad is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:44.72,1:59:48.54,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们搞定了拦截距离的问题，但是相对速度还是不行\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Well, we corrected the intercept range, but we got a problem with intercept velocity.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:48.56,1:59:49.93,Chinese,,0,0,0,,速度差多少?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} How big a problem?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:49.93,1:59:51.92,Chinese,,0,0,0,,42米每秒\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} 42 meters per second.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:51.94,1:59:53.61,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这，\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Well,
Dialogue: 0,1:59:54.11,1:59:55.87,Chinese,,0,0,0,,妈的\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} shit.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:00.48,2:00:02.68,Chinese,,0,0,0,,指挥官，我有个点子\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Commander, I have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:02.68,2:00:04.17,Chinese,,0,0,0,,说吧，mark\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Go ahead, Mark.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:04.20,2:00:07.37,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如果我能找到一个尖锐物\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Well, If I can find something sharp in here
Dialogue: 0,2:00:07.37,2:00:10.37,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我可以在我的宇航服上戳一个洞\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} and poke a hole in the glove of my EVA suit.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:10.37,2:00:13.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,然后就能用溢出的气体的当作助推\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} I could use the escaping air as a thruster
Dialogue: 0,2:00:13.00,2:00:14.54,Chinese,,0,0,0,,然后飞过去找你\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} and fly towards you.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:14.54,2:00:17.88,Chinese,,0,0,0,,应该不会太难操控，我打算在我的胳膊上戳个洞\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} It would be easy to control, because it would be on my arm.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:17.88,2:00:20.01,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我怎么不觉得你能控制得了呢\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} I can't see you having any control if you did that.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:20.04,2:00:24.33,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你只能目测拦截地点，然后你还控制不了助推方向\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} You'd be eyeballing the intercept using a thrust vector you can barely controls
Dialogue: 0,2:00:24.36,2:00:27.92,Chinese,,0,0,0,,没错没错，说的都对\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}  Yes. Yes. Those are all very good points.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:28.30,2:00:31.68,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是，想想看：\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} But, consider this:
Dialogue: 0,2:00:33.07,2:00:36.19,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我就能像钢铁侠一样飞了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}  I'd get to fly around like Iron Man.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:37.23,2:00:38.73,Chinese,,0,0,0,,指挥官\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}  Commander,
Dialogue: 0,2:00:38.75,2:00:40.91,Chinese,,0,0,0,,就这样吧，用钢铁侠计划\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} let's go Iron Man.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:43.45,2:00:45.07,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这可是意料之外\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} This is unexpected, LOS.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:45.10,2:00:47.67,Chinese,,0,0,0,,通讯丢失 待命\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}  Communication lost. Standby.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:47.96,2:00:50.67,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这可能不是一个坏主意\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Maybe it's not the worst idea.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:50.70,2:00:52.71,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不，这就是一个坏主意，不能再坏了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} No, it is the worst idea. It's the worst idea ever.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:52.71,2:00:54.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不是他说的那个\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Not what he said.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:54.00,2:00:57.08,Chinese,,0,0,0,,用大气作为助推\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}  Using atmosphere as thrust.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:58.36,2:01:00.45,Chinese,,0,0,0,,要是把阀门给炸了会怎么样?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} What happens if we blow the VAL?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:00.48,2:01:02.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,什么鬼? 你想打开气密舱?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} What? You want to open the vehicular airlock?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:02.52,2:01:03.69,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这样会给我们一个很不错的减速\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} It'd give us a good kick.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:03.69,2:01:05.38,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是会把飞船的密闭舱给炸掉\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Yeah, but it will also blow the nose off the ship.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:05.40,2:01:08.65,Chinese,,0,0,0,,然后所有的空气就都跑了，然后我们不想死\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} And all the air will leave, and we need air to not die.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:08.67,2:01:11.07,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们可以密封好栈桥和反应室\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} We'll seal the bridge and the reactor room.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:11.09,2:01:13.32,Chinese,,0,0,0,,其他所有地方都变真空\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Everywhere else will go vacuo.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:13.35,2:01:14.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,沃格尔\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Vogel.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:14.41,2:01:15.79,Chinese,,0,0,0,,说吧指挥官\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Go ahead, Commander.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:15.82,2:01:18.80,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我想你回来做一个…炸弹\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} I need you to come inside and make a... bomb.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:18.82,2:01:20.22,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你说什么指挥官?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Uh. Again, Commander?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:20.24,2:01:21.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你是个化学家\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} You're a chemist.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:21.38,2:01:23.98,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你能用飞船上的东西做个炸弹么?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Can you make a bomb with what you have on board?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:24.78,2:01:26.37,Chinese,,0,0,0,,应该行\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Probably.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:27.10,2:01:30.42,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是我觉得应该提醒一下你\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} But I feel obliged to mention that setting off an explosive device
Dialogue: 0,2:01:30.45,2:01:33.68,Chinese,,0,0,0,,在宇航飞船上引爆东西是个坏点子\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} in a spacecraft is a terrible terrible idea.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:33.70,2:01:36.61,Chinese,,0,0,0,,等等 你们不等我回去就要搞炸弹?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Hang on. You guys making a bomb without me?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:36.64,2:01:39.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,懂了，但是你能造个炸弹么?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}  Copy that. Can you do it?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:41.10,2:01:42.54,Chinese,,0,0,0,,可以\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:44.69,2:01:48.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,休斯顿，我们要故意冲破阀门\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Houston. Be advised we're going to deliberately breach the VAL
Dialogue: 0,2:01:48.21,2:01:50.94,Chinese,,0,0,0,,然后提供哦拿一个反向的助推 - 你说什么?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} - to produce some reverse thrust. - What?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:50.97,2:01:53.59,Chinese,,0,0,0,,贝克，别脱你的宇航服，跟约翰森在1号气密舱见面\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Beck, leave your suit on, meet Johanssen in airlock 1.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:53.62,2:01:54.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们将把外面的门打开\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} We'll open the outer door.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:54.93,2:01:57.02,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我需要你把炸弹放在内侧的门上\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} I need you to place the charge on the inner door.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:57.05,2:01:59.27,Chinese,,0,0,0,,然后从外壳爬回2号气密舱\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Climb back to airlock 2 along the hull.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:59.30,2:02:01.81,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好的，我这就过去\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Copy. I'm on my way.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:08.28,2:02:10.01,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我到了，指挥官\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} I'm in, Commander.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:10.03,2:02:11.63,Chinese,,0,0,0,,收到\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Copy that.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:20.21,2:02:21.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,沃格尔，你在哪?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Vogel, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:21.98,2:02:24.57,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 我在厨房 - 好的吧\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} - I'm in the kitchen. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:28.17,2:02:29.38,Chinese,,0,0,0,,指挥官\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Commander,
Dialogue: 0,2:02:29.41,2:02:31.38,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不能让你们尽力这么多，\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} I can't let you go through with this.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:31.38,2:02:33.26,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我准备戳洞了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} I am prepared to cut the suit.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:33.27,2:02:34.47,Chinese,,0,0,0,,别\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:34.47,2:02:37.10,Chinese,,0,0,0,,是这样的, 你看, 我这个人嘛, 很自私\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Well, see. The thing is, I'm selfish.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:37.10,2:02:40.14,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我想回到家之后所有人的纪念都只是关于我的\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} I want all the memorials back home to be about me.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:40.14,2:02:41.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,仅仅纪念我\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Just me.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:41.18,2:02:43.75,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我就不应该来救他\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} I should have left this guy on Mars.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:43.77,2:02:45.15,Chinese,,0,0,0,,嘿！\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Hey.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:47.72,2:02:50.10,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 这是糖? - 没错\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} - Sugar? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:53.91,2:02:55.48,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你能帮我拿一下么?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Can you hold this?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:55.89,2:02:57.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,液氧\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Liquid oxygen.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:57.79,2:03:01.88,Chinese,,0,0,0,,再加一些去渍的, 这里面含有氨\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Add some stain remover that contains ammonia.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:04.56,2:03:06.37,Chinese,,0,0,0,,现在这个玩意\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} This thing here,
Dialogue: 0,2:03:06.61,2:03:09.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,比炸药棒可强5倍呢\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} is 5 times stronger than a stick of dynamite.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:09.78,2:03:11.13,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们怎么引爆他?\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} How do we activate it?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:11.16,2:03:13.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你可以把这个连接到其中一个开关上\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}You can connect this to one of your lighting panels.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:17.69,2:03:19.37,Chinese,,0,0,0,,小心点\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Careful.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:25.23,2:03:27.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,打开1号气密舱\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Open airlock 1.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:32.58,2:03:34.61,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我正在前往贝克的途中\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} I'm on the way to Beck.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:38.03,2:03:40.26,Chinese,,0,0,0,,伙计们，我只希望这是一个好主意\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} I just hope this is a good idea, guys.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:40.28,2:03:42.86,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 这就是 - 打开1号气密舱\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} - It is. - Open A1.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:47.60,2:03:48.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,嗨\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Hi.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:52.51,2:03:54.05,Chinese,,0,0,0,,拿好了吗\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} You have it?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:59.51,2:04:02.75,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你要确保在这个东西爆炸之前离开这里\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Make sure you're not in here when this thing goes off.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:04.08,2:04:05.43,Chinese,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Hey.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:05.43,2:04:07.29,Chinese,,0,0,0,,在太空外面\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Be Careful out there.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:07.32,2:04:09.06,Chinese,,0,0,0,,注意安全\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} In space.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:12.55,2:04:14.62,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不要告诉别人\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Don't tell anyone I did that.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:24.96,2:04:26.64,Chinese,,0,0,0,,炸弹已安放\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Bomb set.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:34.66,2:04:37.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,正在离开1号气密舱\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Leaving airlock 1.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:41.93,2:04:44.79,Chinese,,0,0,0,,伙计们, 我正在计算让阀门爆炸的最佳时间\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} Guys, I'm running the numbers, even with optimum VAL blow,
Dialogue: 0,2:04:44.82,2:04:46.45,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们正在偏离我们的角度\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}We're going to be off on our angle.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:46.48,2:04:49.29,Chinese,,0,0,0,,约翰森, 拦截距离是多少\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&} What's the intercept distance? Johanssen?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:49.31,2:04:51.81,Chinese,,0,0,0,,大约260米\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}260 meters to approximate.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:51.81,2:04:53.69,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这太远了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}It's too far.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:02.16,2:05:03.58,Chinese,,0,0,0,,指挥官\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Commander?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:03.58,2:05:05.97,Chinese,,0,0,0,,马丁内斯, 离门近点\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Martinez, close the door.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:08.56,2:05:10.49,Chinese,,0,0,0,,打开D3\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Open D3.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:11.02,2:05:12.78,Chinese,,0,0,0,,让它一直开着\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Leave it open.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:41.35,2:05:43.41,Chinese,,0,0,0,,打开B2\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Open B2.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:47.34,2:05:48.58,Chinese,,0,0,0,,约翰森\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Johanssen,
Dialogue: 0,2:05:48.58,2:05:51.08,Chinese,,0,0,0,,距离阀门还有多久爆炸\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Time to VAL blow after initiate?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:51.08,2:05:52.55,Chinese,,0,0,0,,15秒\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}15 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:52.57,2:05:55.13,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们知道如何拉近距离\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}We sure know how to cut it close.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:55.57,2:05:56.59,Chinese,,0,0,0,,指挥官\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Commander.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:56.62,2:05:59.47,Chinese,,0,0,0,,距离太远了, 我要出去了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}The distance is too far, I'm going out.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:59.49,2:06:01.44,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 我可以做到的 - 这可不是比赛\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- I can do this. - It's not a debate.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:01.47,2:06:03.51,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我是不会拿我的船员的生命冒险的\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I'm not risking another crew member.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:03.53,2:06:05.04,Chinese,,0,0,0,,贝克回来了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Beck's returned.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:05.06,2:06:07.12,Chinese,,0,0,0,,约翰森, 还有多久引爆炸弹\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Johanssen, initiate the bomb.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:07.15,2:06:08.54,Chinese,,0,0,0,,10秒\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}10 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:08.57,2:06:10.19,Chinese,,0,0,0,,系上安全带\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Strap in.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:10.22,2:06:11.58,Chinese,,0,0,0,,5秒\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}5.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:11.88,2:06:13.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,4秒\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}4.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:13.38,2:06:14.07,Chinese,,0,0,0,,3秒\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}3.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:14.07,2:06:16.63,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 减速 - 2秒\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- Deceleration! - 2,
Dialogue: 0,2:06:16.74,2:06:17.47,Chinese,,0,0,0,,1秒\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}1.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:17.49,2:06:19.83,Chinese,,0,0,0,,激活控制板41\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Activating the panel 41.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:40.92,2:06:42.44,Chinese,,0,0,0,,封锁舱安全\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Bridge seal holding.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:42.47,2:06:44.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 有什么损伤 - 先不用担心这个\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- What's the damage? - Worry about that later.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:44.72,2:06:46.43,Chinese,,0,0,0,,相对加速度是多少\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}What's the relative velocity?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:46.43,2:06:47.99,Chinese,,0,0,0,,12米每秒\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}12 meters per second.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:48.01,2:06:49.63,Chinese,,0,0,0,,收到\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Copy.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:51.94,2:06:53.57,Chinese,,0,0,0,,把我绑起来\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Hook me up.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:54.44,2:06:56.02,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Done.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:05.50,2:07:07.59,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我看到了飞行器\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I've visual of the MAV.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:08.62,2:07:10.51,Chinese,,0,0,0,,拦截距离是多少\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}What's the intercept range?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:10.54,2:07:12.25,Chinese,,0,0,0,,正在查\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I'm checking.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:12.74,2:07:14.30,Chinese,,0,0,0,,312米\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}312 meters.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:14.30,2:07:16.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你刚才是说312米吗\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Did you say 312?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:16.92,2:07:19.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好的, 我到了向你们招手\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Okay. I'll wave at you guys as I go by.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:22.61,2:07:23.98,Chinese,,0,0,0,,哦\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:28.43,2:07:30.73,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我够不着你, 马克 你离我太远了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I can't get to you, Mark. You're too far.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:30.75,2:07:32.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 我抓不住你 - 我知道\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- I'm not going to make it - I know.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:32.79,2:07:34.93,Chinese,,0,0,0,,贝克, 把我解绑 我要跟着他\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Beck, unhook me. I'm going after him.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:34.95,2:07:37.93,Chinese,,0,0,0,,指挥官, 我能搞定\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Commander, I got this.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:51.24,2:07:53.05,Chinese,,0,0,0,,马克, 请汇报\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Mark, report.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:53.15,2:07:55.15,Chinese,,0,0,0,,马上就来, 指挥官\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}On my way, Commander.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:55.17,2:07:56.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,该死\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:05.93,2:08:08.43,Chinese,,0,0,0,,约翰森, 我对马克的相对速度是多少\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Johanssen, what's my relative velocity to Mark?
Dialogue: 0,2:08:08.43,2:08:10.47,Chinese,,0,0,0,,5.2 米每秒\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}5.2 meters per second.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:10.47,2:08:12.99,Chinese,,0,0,0,,收到 正在调整\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Copy. Adjusting course.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:17.91,2:08:20.43,Chinese,,0,0,0,,3.1 米每秒\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}3.1 meters per second.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:22.26,2:08:25.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,距离目标还有24米\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Distance to target 24 meters.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:26.24,2:08:28.75,Chinese,,0,0,0,,还有11米\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}11 meters to target.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:31.08,2:08:32.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,6米\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}6 meters.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:43.22,2:08:44.98,Chinese,,0,0,0,,坚持住, 马克\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Hold on, Mark.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:05.84,2:09:07.39,Chinese,,0,0,0,,来\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:12.51,2:09:14.07,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我抓住他了!\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I got him!
Dialogue: 0,2:09:16.38,2:09:17.93,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我抓住他了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I got him.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:18.78,2:09:19.93,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我抓住他了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I got him.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:19.96,2:09:22.06,Chinese,,0,0,0,,做得好, 钢铁侠\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Way to go, Iron Man.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:24.70,2:09:26.83,Chinese,,0,0,0,,贝克, 拉我们进去\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Beck, pull us in.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:29.46,2:09:31.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,很高兴见到你\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}It's good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:32.88,2:09:34.30,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你……\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}You...
Dialogue: 0,2:09:35.79,2:09:38.19,Chinese,,0,0,0,,的音乐品味……\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}have... terrible taste
Dialogue: 0,2:09:38.21,2:09:39.83,Chinese,,0,0,0,,太烂了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}in music.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:48.67,2:09:51.02,Chinese,,0,0,0,,休斯顿, 这里是赫尔墨斯行动\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Houston, this is Hermes Actual.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:51.05,2:09:52.12,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们接上他了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}We got him.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:52.15,2:09:53.52,Chinese,,0,0,0,,耶!\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}YEAH!
Dialogue: 0,2:09:53.54,2:09:55.41,Chinese,,0,0,0,,沃特尼安全了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Watney is secure.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:55.44,2:09:58.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好! 好! 好!\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}YES! YES! YES!
Dialogue: 0,2:10:00.52,2:10:02.86,Chinese,,0,0,0,,和外太空的马克·沃特尼联系上了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Contact in outer space, with Mark Watney.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:02.89,2:10:07.21,Chinese,,0,0,0,,历时良久, 他们终于完成了许多人所认为的不可能\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}After a very long time, they have done what many people thought was impossible.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:07.24,2:10:11.03,Chinese,,0,0,0,,特别庆祝：马克·沃特尼成功获救\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Special Gratulation: Mark Watney has been successfully rescued.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:11.06,2:10:14.66,Chinese,,0,0,0,,马克·沃特尼获救了, 这是一次不可思议的任务\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Mark Watney has been rescued. This has been an incredible mission.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:14.69,2:10:16.60,Chinese,,0,0,0,,抓住他\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Get a hold of him.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:18.44,2:10:19.71,Chinese,,0,0,0,,嘿嘿, 帅哥\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Hey- Hey, handsome.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:19.74,2:10:21.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,贝克, 把舱门关上\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Beck, close the hatch.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:24.56,2:10:26.41,Chinese,,0,0,0,,嘿, 各位!\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Hey, guys!
Dialogue: 0,2:10:30.32,2:10:34.04,Chinese,,0,0,0,,休斯顿, 6名成员安全上船\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Houston, 6 crews safely aboard.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:37.28,2:10:40.30,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这是个伟大的时刻, 对于国家, 对于世界\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}This is a huge moment for this nation, for the world
Dialogue: 0,2:10:40.33,2:10:43.83,Chinese,,0,0,0,,当然, 对于国际太空旅行来说亦然\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}and, in deed, for international space travel.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:46.73,2:10:48.62,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 嘿 - 嘿\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- Hey. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:49.93,2:10:51.73,Chinese,,0,0,0,,天哪!\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Oh god!
Dialogue: 0,2:10:53.63,2:10:55.44,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你耽误了不少工夫啊, 哥们儿\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}There's a little sloth going on over there, man.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:55.46,2:10:59.11,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我知道, 都一年半没洗澡了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}I know. I haven't had a shower for a year and a half.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:59.29,2:11:02.44,Chinese,,0,0,0,,别逗我笑, 我断了根肋骨\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Don't make me laugh. I have a broken rib.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:35.80,2:11:37.27,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你好啊\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Hey, there.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:45.50,2:11:46.81,Chinese,,0,0,0,,日安, 长官\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Good day, sir.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:46.83,2:11:49.06,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 真是荣幸, 长官 - 长官好\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- It's an honor, sir. - Sir.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:49.32,2:11:51.17,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 长官好 - 长官好\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- Sir. - Sir.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:51.20,2:11:52.89,Chinese,,0,0,0,,早安, 长官\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Good morning, sir.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:14.37,2:12:17.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到宇航员预备计划\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Welcome to the Astronaut Candidate Program.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:17.20,2:12:21.19,Chinese,,0,0,0,,现在请注意听, 因为可能会救你一命\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Now pay attention, because this could save your life.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:21.21,2:12:23.63,Chinese,,0,0,0,,相信我, 我很懂自己在说什么\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Trust me. I know what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:24.09,2:12:26.29,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好, 让我先把几件事说清楚, 就现在\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Alright. Let me get a few things out of the way, right off the bat.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:26.32,2:12:32.92,Chinese,,0,0,0,,是的, 我确实在一个荒芜的星球上活下来了, 靠着用自己的屎种地\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Yes, I did in fact survive on a deserted planet by farming in my own shit.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:33.42,2:12:38.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,是的, 其实比听起来更糟糕, 所以, 咱们还是别再提这茬了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Yes, it's actually worse than it sound. So, let's not talk about that ever again.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:38.95,2:12:42.06,Chinese,,0,0,0,,另一个我常被问及的是\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}The other question I get most frequently is.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:42.13,2:12:44.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,当我在那里, 孑然一身\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}When I was up there stranded by myself,
Dialogue: 0,2:12:44.74,2:12:46.94,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我想过会死去吗？\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Did I think I was going to die?
Dialogue: 0,2:12:47.69,2:12:49.92,Chinese,,0,0,0,,是的, 当然\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Yes, absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:50.31,2:12:53.69,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而且这是你在加入的时候就要知道的, 因为这会发生在你身上\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}And that's what you need to know going in, because it's going to happen to you.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:53.72,2:12:57.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这是太空, 它不会顺着你\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}This is space. It does not cooperate.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:57.39,2:13:00.31,Chinese,,0,0,0,,有时候, 就会屋漏偏逢连夜雨\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}At some point, everything's going to go south on you.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:00.31,2:13:03.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,屋漏偏逢连夜雨, 你会说：“就这样了”\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Everything's going to go south and you're going to say "This is it."
Dialogue: 0,2:13:03.39,2:13:05.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我就这么完了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}That is how I end.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:06.48,2:13:08.42,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这时你要么接受\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Now you can either accept that,
Dialogue: 0,2:13:08.45,2:13:10.37,Chinese,,0,0,0,,要么去工作\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}or you can get to work.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:11.49,2:13:13.41,Chinese,,0,0,0,,就是这么回事\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}That's all it is.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:13.43,2:13:15.79,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你只要开始\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}You just begin.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:16.04,2:13:19.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你算算数, 解决掉一个问题\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}You do the math. You solve one problem
Dialogue: 0,2:13:19.21,2:13:21.14,Chinese,,0,0,0,,然后你解决下一个\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}and you solve the next one,
Dialogue: 0,2:13:21.17,2:13:22.15,Chinese,,0,0,0,,然后又一个\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}and then the next.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:22.17,2:13:24.96,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如果你解决足够多的问题, 你就能回家了\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}And If you solve enough problems, you get to come home.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:25.86,2:13:28.43,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好, 有问题吗？\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Alright. Questions?
Dialogue: 0,2:13:32.81,2:13:35.49,Chinese,,0,0,0,,一旦指挥中心完成了飞行前检查\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Once Mission Control complete their preflight checks,
Dialogue: 0,2:13:35.52,2:13:37.58,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们就开始发射程序\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}we'll begin launch procedures.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:37.61,2:13:40.27,Chinese,,0,0,0,,阿瑞斯5号将与赫尔墨斯号对接\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}The Ares 5 team will rendezvous with the Hermes
Dialogue: 0,2:13:40.30,2:13:43.48,Chinese,,0,0,0,,约于发射后48分钟\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}approximately 48 minutes after launch.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:43.51,2:13:47.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,从那时起, 他们将进行为期414天的太空旅行\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}From there, they'll have 414 days of space travel ahead of them.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:47.40,2:13:51.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,阿瑞斯5号较之前任务, 目标有所改变吗？\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Have the goals changed from the previous mission to the Ares 5 program?
Dialogue: 0,2:13:51.39,2:13:53.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,以及你们本次希望有何成就？\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}And what do you hope to achieve this time around?
Dialogue: 0,2:13:53.71,2:13:57.86,Chinese,,0,0,0,,嗯, 不, 阿瑞斯计划的目标从未改变\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Well, no. The goals has always been the same for the Ares Program.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:58.16,2:14:02.03,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这次, 当然, 我们希望一次就能把所有宇航员带回来\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}This time, of course we hope to bring all the astronauts back at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:02.05,2:14:05.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,- 指挥, 引导人员检查完毕 - 收到, 引导人员\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}- Flight, Guidance check complete. - Copy, Guidance.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:05.42,2:14:09.58,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我是指挥, 我们按时发射\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}This is Flight. We are go for launch on schedule.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:19.65,2:14:22.11,Chinese,,0,0,0,,最后一次航空服务检查完毕\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Final Aerial Service Check are complete.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:22.14,2:14:25.87,Chinese,,0,0,0,,万事俱备, 只欠发射\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}As everything remains a go. Fvor the launch of the Ares 5.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:25.90,2:14:27.45,Chinese,,0,0,0,,20秒\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}20 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:28.44,2:14:30.25,Chinese,,0,0,0,,继续倒数\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Proceeding with the count.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:30.28,2:14:31.97,Chinese,,0,0,0,,倒计时10\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}T minus 10.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:32.00,2:14:33.08,Chinese,,0,0,0,,9\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}9.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:33.11,2:14:34.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,主引擎点火\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Main engine start.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:34.43,2:14:38.38,Chinese,,0,0,0,,7, 6, 5, 4\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}7, 6, 5, 4,
Dialogue: 0,2:14:38.41,2:14:41.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,3, 2, 1\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}3, 2, 1.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:41.79,2:14:43.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,升空\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}And liftoff.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:43.26,2:14:49.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,此时, 阿瑞斯5号的成员开启了美国太空探索新的一页\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}As the crew of the Ares 5 begin the next chapter of America's space exploration.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:49.50,2:14:51.30,Chinese,,0,0,0,,压力正常\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Pressure look good.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:52.74,2:14:54.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,呜!\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Woo!
Dialogue: 0,2:15:09.49,2:15:11.11,Chinese,,0,0,0,,哇, 漂亮\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}Wow, good shot.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:11.11,2:15:14.87,Chinese,,0,0,0,,终于, 在解救宇航员马克·沃特尼5年后\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}There it is. 5 years after the rescue of astronaut Mark Watney,
Dialogue: 0,2:15:14.87,2:15:18.53,Chinese,,0,0,0,,阿瑞斯5号奔向了火星\N{\fs15\3c&H000000&}the Ares 5 is on it's way to Mars.
